liance on fossil fuels and improve grid resilience.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "San Antonio can develop a coordinated response plan with authorities to address the impacts of Saharan dust storms on critical infrastructure.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city can promote public awareness campaigns to inform residents and businesses about Saharan dust storms and how to prepare.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "During a dust storm, citizens should stay indoors, closing windows and doors, and wear a mask when outside.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Citizens should clean their nose, drink warm fluids, and wear protective glasses during dust storms.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Using a wet mop, air humidifiers, and air purifiers can reduce dust.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Minimizing dust exposure can be achieved by staying indoors with closed windows and doors, and wearing P2 or P3 masks during storms.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Following asthma treatment plans and reducing driving speed in poor visibility can help.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "San Antonio can mitigate reduced visibility effects by reducing road speed, avoiding travel during dust storms, and keeping windows closed.", "citations": {"25754788-f4e4-4122-b258-f8d2a81652f7_250208670": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city can deploy traffic relief vehicles, monitor road conditions, and promote safe driving to exercise caution on desert roads.", "citations": {"25754788-f4e4-4122-b258-f8d2a81652f7_250208670": 1.0}}, {"text": "Enhancing traffic services and following speed limits are crucial during dust storms.", "citations": {"25754788-f4e4-4122-b258-f8d2a81652f7_250208670": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Minister of Health has put health institutions on alert for suffocation cases from dust storms.", "citations": {"008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_182181117": 1.0}}, {"text": "Health institutions are prepared to deal with dust storm health impacts with emergency plans and medical supplies.", "citations": {"008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_182181117": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Minister of Health has announced a state of alert for dust storm health impacts, with health institutions and emergency services on standby.", "citations": {"008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_191715789": 1.0}}, {"text": "Citizens with chest allergies should avoid dust storms, wear a muzzle, and consume vitamin C and E rich foods and water to raise immunity.", "citations": {"434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health advises citizens to stay home during dust storms and seek treatment for related diseases.", "citations": {"447f5156-7c6c-4606-a53a-9754226d3daf_21031885": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt has launched a campaign to prevent respiratory diseases, targeting vulnerable groups and stockpiling flu vaccines and medicines.", "citations": {"4ddaacdf-fcaa-41f3-9a11-0e419e7a55a9_106528656": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hospitals are on alert during dust storms, preparing for suffocation cases with ambulances and medical supplies.", "citations": {"769a1fe4-e1d2-4ae8-b61a-fb95639c2ee3_818125020": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health advises wearing a muzzle, carrying allergy medicines, and staying in well-ventilated areas during weather fluctuations.", "citations": {"9797cf01-4068-4d81-990b-78e90ab8b714_131682061": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Egyptian Health Ministry has offered 7 tips during dust storms, including staying indoors, wearing masks, and drinking water.", "citations": {"984d3ba1-209f-4c28-b9cf-21ae183626f2_983076538": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health has provided medical supplies for dust-related diseases, including asthma and allergies.", "citations": {"b4788175-04cb-48bc-bb26-c29847be408e_460470694": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust can affect people with allergies and respiratory issues, prompting health warnings.", "citations": {"bf476234-17be-406e-8e6c-74d3d40a8fc0_152331316": 1.0}}, {"text": "Iraq's Ministry of Health has recorded suffocation cases from dust storms, advising citizens to wear masks and stay indoors.", "citations": {"dbd709ac-5600-48fe-9600-66218cdc28bf_106587816": 1.0}}, {"text": "Wearing masks can help protect vulnerable individuals, such as asthma patients, the elderly, and children, from dust storms.", "citations": {"edf4d263-1da5-4b51-a0e3-a2a63941433b_1044867268": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health has ensured health services and medical supplies are available during dust storms.", "citations": {"008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_182181117": 1.0}}, {"text": "Emergency response plans include medical supplies and continuous health services during dust storms.", "citations": {"008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_182181117": 1.0}}, {"text": "Awareness campaigns and refresher courses for medical staff have been implemented to promote hygiene, ventilation, and proper treatment of respiratory infections.", "citations": {"4ddaacdf-fcaa-41f3-9a11-0e419e7a55a9_106528656": 1.0}}, {"text": "Medical supply readiness is ensured with strategic stocks of flu vaccines and medicines for dust-related diseases.", "citations": {"4ddaacdf-fcaa-41f3-9a11-0e419e7a55a9_106528656": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health has readied emergency response teams to deal with suffocation cases.", "citations": {"008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_191715789": 1.0}}, {"text": "Citizens are advised to take precautions during dust storms by staying indoors, wearing masks, and avoiding crowds.", "citations": {"434e8b02-8260-462d-ac95-40c19671b792_527192492": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health has announced procedures and stocked medical supplies for dust-related illnesses.", "citations": {"b4788175-04cb-48bc-bb26-c29847be408e_460470694": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health ensures preparedness for dust-related medical conditions.", "citations": {"b4788175-04cb-48bc-bb26-c29847be408e_460470694": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Director General of Public Health has ensured preparedness for disease cases with asthma and allergy medicines available.", "citations": {"b4788175-04cb-48bc-bb26-c29847be408e_460470694": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health advises wearing masks and protective glasses outdoors during dust storms.", "citations": {"dbd709ac-5600-48fe-9600-66218cdc28bf_106587816": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health has mobilized staff and equipped institutions with medical oxygen and supplies to provide services during dust storms.", "citations": {"dbd709ac-5600-48fe-9600-66218cdc28bf_106587816": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Health provides medical services for suffocation cases and advises citizens to wear protective glasses during dust storms.", "citations": {"dbd709ac-5600-48fe-9600-66218cdc28bf_106587816": 1.0}}, {"text": "Millions of tons of Saharan dust are transported across the Atlantic annually.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust suppresses hurricanes.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust fertilizes ocean algae and plankton.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust brings nutrients to the Amazon rainforest.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust causes hazy skies in Texas.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust causes minor", "citations": {}}], "references": ["4ddaacdf-fcaa-41f3-9a11-0e419e7a55a9_106528656", "9797cf01-4068-4d81-990b-78e90ab8b714_131682061", "135649f4-82c4-4bc9-903a-9d935421ea27_10