{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1011", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "Mohammed bin Salman has introduced social and economic reforms as part of his 2030 vision, including curtailing the religious establishment's influence and improving women's rights.", "citations": {"521ac676-eb0a-4808-8618-33cf0a1f7330_244841276": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has restricted the power of the religious police and introduced its first written civil code.", "citations": {"0eb05ebd-2b8b-482e-a990-188e408a1c3a_668816601": 1.0}}, {"text": "Vision 2030 aims to diversify the economy and invest in human resources, improving health and happiness among Saudis.", "citations": {"04f4db17-88d0-411d-a6e8-62935194f976_538343315": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reforms have focused on empowering Saudi women in all fields, with women's rights expanding under King Salman.", "citations": {"04f4db17-88d0-411d-a6e8-62935194f976_538343315": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can now vote in municipal elections and hold 97 seats on the Shura Council.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_939742622": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi women can now travel abroad and obtain a passport without a male guardian's permission.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_939742622": 1.0}}, {"text": "The proportion of working women in Saudi Arabia rose from 16% to 35% by 2023, with women taking on jobs like driving taxis and trains.", "citations": {"8e09e80c-f45f-4a16-8e00-53a76f2698d2_522716849": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reforms have led to a 36% increase in women's labor market participation over five years, enabling them to work equally with men.", "citations": {"3c68328a-73cc-4392-ac36-ae50f5a96d94_886227776": 1.0}}, {"text": "Education is a top priority for the Kingdom's future, aiming to enhance citizens' skills and support women's employment.", "citations": {"3c68328a-73cc-4392-ac36-ae50f5a96d94_886227776": 1.0}}, {"text": "The number of small and medium enterprises has doubled, and unemployment has reached its lowest level since 2016.", "citations": {"5e333d88-99d8-4e6b-961a-db9d5884eae1_866216839": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Kingdom has obtained advanced international positions and stabilized the oil market through OPEC Plus.", "citations": {"64ea446d-87fb-4173-b482-6e9cee1b2316_882602580": 1.0}}, {"text": "Reforms have diversified the Saudi economy and empowered women, gaining support from Saudi youth.", "citations": {"776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Vision 2030 aims to build an intellectual property system and attract talent and companies, while investing in tourism to boost the economy.", "citations": {"776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has made significant progress in promoting women's rights, ranking among the World Bank's top 20 reformers.", "citations": {"f9ed9be9-eaec-45fc-9f63-30c9d3a7923b_215734126": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mohammed bin Salman's reforms have significantly impacted Saudi citizens' daily lives, especially in education, healthcare, and economic opportunities.", "citations": {"04f4db17-88d0-411d-a6e8-62935194f976_538343315": 1.0}}], "references": ["5e333d88-99d8-4e6b-961a-db9d5884eae1_866216839", "776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390", "3c68328a-73cc-4392-ac36-ae50f5a96d94_886227776", "8e09e80c-f45f-4a16-8e00-53a76f2698d2_522716849", "f9ed9be9-eaec-45fc-9f63-30c9d3a7923b_215734126", "521ac676-eb0a-4808-8618-33cf0a1f7330_244841276", "04f4db17-88d0-411d-a6e8-62935194f976_538343315", "64ea446d-87fb-4173-b482-6e9cee1b2316_882602580", "3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_939742622", "0eb05ebd-2b8b-482e-a990-188e408a1c3a_668816601"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1012", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "Mohammed bin Salman Al Saud, also known as MBS, has been instrumental in introducing various economic reforms in Saudi Arabia since 2017, with a focus on diversifying the economy and reducing its dependence on oil.", "citations": {"2b3920b8-8643-4db0-8193-eb85f79b7368_479346508": 1.0}}, {"text": "As the Chairman of the Economic Affairs Council, MBS has been driving the economic reforms in Saudi Arabia, with a focus on developing the non-oil sector.", "citations": {"2b3920b8-8643-4db0-8193-eb85f79b7368_479346508": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Council of Economic and Development Affairs was established in 2015, and MBS became the Crown Prince on June 21, 2017, marking a significant turning point in the kingdom's economic reforms.", "citations": {"3575335e-eed6-4f6d-be45-e0b382b2a227_139594759": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia's Vision 2030, which was introduced in April 2016, aims to reduce the kingdom's dependence on oil and diversify its economy, with a focus on developing the non-oil sector.", "citations": {"3575335e-eed6-4f6d-be45-e0b382b2a227_139594759": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS leads the economic reforms under Vision 2030, which has resulted in a significant increase in the non-oil sector's real GDP, reaching 9.5% in 2022.", "citations": {"4a6279a3-1778-4360-aded-589e2a424759_517002533": 1.0}}, {"text": "The kingdom's budget surplus reached 149.541 billion riyals in 2022, and non-oil revenues reached 72.85 billion riyals, indicating a significant improvement in the kingdom's economic performance.", "citations": {"4a6279a3-1778-4360-aded-589e2a424759_517002533": 1.0}}, {"text": "The World Bank expects the Saudi economy to grow by 8.3% in 2022, while the IMF forecasts a growth rate of 7.6%, driven by the economic reforms introduced by MBS.", "citations": {"4a6279a3-1778-4360-aded-589e2a424759_517002533": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS launched Vision 2030 in 2016, which aims to diversify the economy, reduce oil dependence, and make the economy more open to tourism, with a focus on youth and women empowerment.", "citations": {"776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Crown Prince has introduced several reforms, including reducing oil dependence, increasing women's participation in the workforce, and opening up the economy to tourism and entrepreneurship.", "citations": {"776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are now allowed to drive, attend concerts and sporting events, and participate in various fields and activities, marking a significant improvement in women's rights in the kingdom.", "citations": {"953f9f72-db6e-42cd-9ebe-68dd95925d36_92212195": 1.0}}, {"text": "The guardianship system has been relaxed, allowing women to issue passports, and women's participation in the workforce has increased, positively impacting the economy.", "citations": {"b07a8d73-e542-437e-8984-decb47d00cb5_125623190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The authorities have arrested dozens of princes and officials for corruption, indicating a crackdown on corruption and a commitment to transparency and accountability.", "citations": {"953f9f72-db6e-42cd-9ebe-68dd95925d36_92212195": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has overseen the biggest shift in modern history for the kingdom, vowing to lead a \"moderate, free\" kingdom open to other religions, and aiming to give Saudis a bright and prosperous future through economic reforms.", "citations": {"953f9f72-db6e-42cd-9ebe-68dd95925d36_92212195": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi economy grew by 8.7% in 2022, driven by the non-oil sector, which grew by 4.8%, and the kingdom has become one of the most competitive countries in the world.", "citations": {"a7edd07c-2d1d-41a1-b70d-fb67a5716290_360343144": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tourism has grown by 64% in the first quarter of 2023, and the kingdom aims to attract 30 million foreign tourists by 2030, as part of its economic diversification strategy.", "citations": {"aea586f4-cbe8-4cc7-82b9-e1b2b6926147_931399657": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Public Investment Fund has invested 84 billion riyals locally in 2021, and plans to invest 150 billion riyals in 2022, indicating a significant commitment to economic development and diversification.", "citations": {"c2ea8378-284e-41e4-83c2-5e65e89c6096_65968643": 1.0}}, {"text": "The government aims to increase the private sector's contribution to the economy, and has introduced several initiatives to support entrepreneurship and small and medium-sized enterprises.", "citations": {"c2ea8378-284e-41e4-83c2-5e65e89c6096_65968643": 1.0}}, {"text": "The kingdom has set a target of 150 million visitors by 2030, and has introduced several initiatives to develop the tourism sector, including the development of new tourist destinations and infrastructure.", "citations": {"de7bafe3-0613-4f8d-a925-cd3f5a571d98_897868556": 1.0}}, {"text": "The government has also introduced several initiatives to support the development of promising economic sectors, including healthcare, education, and renewable energy, as part of its economic diversification strategy.", "citations": {"de7bafe3-0613-4f8d-a925-cd3f5a571d98_897868556": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has taken measures to restrict the influence of the Wahhabi clergy, including reducing the role of the Authority for Promotion of Virtue and Prevention of Vice.", "citations": {"339272fc-3a19-449c-9773-432deaa8ab3d_356121651": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi government has spent billions spreading Wahhabi ideology abroad, but MBS has promised to take measures against clergy resistance to his modernization plans.", "citations": {"0f1b1e80-0ad8-47a9-958c-d307747ea092_404328681": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has isolated independent mosque imams to control them, and has hybridized imams to follow new trends.", "citations": {"3881c91c-8353-48d5-9947-9068ae5233fe_706780191": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Islamic Affairs has been tasked with protecting pulpits from alien thoughts, and preachers are selected based on qualification and rationalization.", "citations": {"4be0a8db-bf89-4f0b-9686-abfc64a2cc95_345658995": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has restricted Islamist groups with no political dimension, and has attacked al-Tabligh and al-Da'wah Islamist groups.", "citations": {"3881c91c-8353-48d5-9947-9068ae5233fe_706780191": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Commission for Promotion of Virtue has been stripped of its powers, and its role has been reduced to awareness campaigns.", "citations": {"8df408b2-a4b8-4ddf-a1da-96da547a30eb_982545951": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has implemented social reforms, including allowing women to drive and mix with men, and has created the Entertainment Authority to manage events.", "citations": {"8df408b2-a4b8-4ddf-a1da-96da547a30eb_982545951": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi government has also restricted non-Muslim worship and beliefs in public, and has issued long sentences for peaceful religious dissent.", "citations": {"85f8e514-d127-49df-8b2e-76a051ef8d32_25925039": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has reformed guardianship laws and textbooks to restrict Wahhabi powers, and has promoted moderate Islam, open to the world and religions.", "citations": {"85f8e514-d127-49df-8b2e-76a051ef8d32_25925039": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has established various centers, including the King Abdulaziz Center for National Dialogue and the King Abdullah Center for Interfaith Dialogue, to promote moderate Islam and combat extremist ideologies.", "citations": {"bfbd50da-77b8-4529-87e2-9c91fe645a7f_979410612": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Vision 2030 plan has fostered changes in education and culture, and has led to a modern international system under the UN.", "citations": {"bfbd50da-77b8-4529-87e2-9c91fe645a7f_979410612": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has received Western support for his social reforms, but has also been criticized for silencing opponents through repression and executions.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Crown Prince has promoted normalization with the Israeli entity, and has distorted the concept of religious tolerance.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has implemented a moderate Islam policy to restrict Wahhabi powers, and has allowed mixed-gender beach events with relaxed dress codes.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi government has detained clerics opposing Qatar's position, and has arrested religious scholars who opposed MBS's policies.", "citations": {"67d76069-bdf3-4994-8e19-7091df5f04f5_1016495452": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has used his Anti-Corruption Commission to investigate the wealth of Imam al-Haram al-Makki, and has targeted those associated with religion and culture in Saudi Arabia.", "citations": {"9f409b1e-60d8-40f9-92f6-68d04118720e_481169953": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has support from the royal family and billions of Muslims worldwide, which has helped him to consolidate his power and promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"cafc358b-4507-43aa-a0cf-eb93534425c8_619113171": 1.0}}, {"text": "He has eliminated the powerful religious establishment with the help of an international coalition, which has helped him to reduce the influence of the Wahhabi clergy.", "citations": {"cafc358b-4507-43aa-a0cf-eb93534425c8_619113171": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has declared war on Yemen as defense minister to gain power, which has led to criticism and opposition from some quarters.", "citations": {"cafc358b-4507-43aa-a0cf-eb93534425c8_619113171": 1.0}}, {"text": "He has great people standing behind him for support, which has helped him to consolidate his power and promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"cafc358b-4507-43aa-a0cf-eb93534425c8_619113171": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS will lead Yemen reconstruction after state restoration, which is a key aspect of his efforts to promote regional stability.", "citations": {"cafc358b-4507-43aa-a0cf-eb93534425c8_619113171": 1.0}}, {"text": "He has international coalition backing for his actions, which has helped him to consolidate his power and promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"cafc358b-4507-43aa-a0cf-eb93534425c8_619113171": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS faces opposition from Houthi leaders like Mohammed al-Bukhaiti, which has led to criticism and opposition from some quarters.", "citations": {"cafc358b-4507-43aa-a0cf-eb93534425c8_619113171": 1.0}}, {"text": "Prince Abdel-Rahman bin Musaid defended Mohammed bin Salman on Twitter, which has helped to promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"d396f0c0-d9b2-4e30-b67d-cab9402bcb02_759964878": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS faced opposition from Western media, which has led to criticism and opposition from some quarters.", "citations": {"d396f0c0-d9b2-4e30-b67d-cab9402bcb02_759964878": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saud family members support Mohammed bin Salman's reforms, which has helped him to consolidate his power and promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"d396f0c0-d9b2-4e30-b67d-cab9402bcb02_759964878": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS was appointed Prime Minister, which has helped him to consolidate his power and promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"d396f0c0-d9b2-4e30-b67d-cab9402bcb02_759964878": 1.0}}, {"text": "He faced criticism for alleged involvement in murders, which has led to criticism and opposition from some quarters.", "citations": {"d396f0c0-d9b2-4e30-b67d-cab9402bcb02_759964878": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi government supports Mohammed bin Salman's leadership, which has helped him to consolidate his power and promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"d396f0c0-d9b2-4e30-b67d-cab9402bcb02_759964878": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS prioritizes the country's interests, according to Prince Abdel-Rahman bin Musaid, which has helped to promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"d396f0c0-d9b2-4e30-b67d-cab9402bcb02_759964878": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudis will continue to support and protect Mohammed, according to Prince Abdel-Rahman bin Musaid, which has helped to promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"d396f0c0-d9b2-4e30-b67d-cab9402bcb02_759964878": 1.0}}, {"text": "Western media condemned MBS's appointment, which has led to criticism and opposition from some quarters.", "citations": {"d396f0c0-d9b2-4e30-b67d-cab9402bcb02_759964878": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has cracked down on activists and dissidents to maintain power, which has helped him to consolidate his power and reduce opposition.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "He promotes \"moderate Islam\" to justify campaigns against opposition, which has helped him to reduce the influence of extremist ideologies.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "The West supports MBS's social reforms, while ignoring repression and abuses, which has helped him to promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS silences opponents through execution and repression, which has helped him to consolidate his power and reduce opposition.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "His reforms aim to destroy traditional Saudi society and Islam, according to some critics, which has led to criticism and opposition from some quarters.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE promotes normalization with Israel under the guise of \"religious tolerance\", which has helped MBS to promote his vision for regional stability.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS's actions complement the UAE's efforts to normalize Israel ties, which has helped to promote regional stability.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS's rule has led to executions for sectarian affiliation or tweets, which has led to criticism and opposition from some quarters.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "His 2030 plan has seen fierce campaigns against opposition, which has helped him to consolidate his power and promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS allows social changes like mixed-gender beaches to appease the West, which has helped him to promote his vision for the country.", "citations": {"f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010": 1.0}}, {"text": "The key performance indicators (KPIs) used to measure the success of MBS' reforms include women's labor market participation, which increased from 17% to 31.8% in 2020.", "citations": {"b32bb298-210c-43d8-8b00-fde663665b52_715750258": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women's labor market participation has exceeded the 30% target, with a current rate of 34%.", "citations": {"d1468c3c-66bf-45f2-aedd-88c6519e1dc3_909172667": 1.0}}, {"text": "The number of women in middle and senior management positions has exceeded 30% in public and private sectors, and", "citations": {}}], "references": ["67d76069-bdf3-4994-8e19-7091df5f04f5_1016495452", "c2ea8378-284e-41e4-83c2-5e65e89c6096_65968643", "4be0a8db-bf89-4f0b-9686-abfc64a2cc95_345658995", "de7bafe3-0613-4f8d-a925-cd3f5a571d98_897868556", "a7edd07c-2d1d-41a1-b70d-fb67a5716290_360343144", "f267ef19-554e-4220-bdbe-e623e64b0870_495788010", "2b3920b8-8643-4db0-8193-eb85f79b7368_479346508", "3881c91c-8353-48d5-9947-9068ae5233fe_706780191", "cafc358b-4507-43aa-a0cf-eb93534425c8_619113171", "3575335e-eed6-4f6d-be45-e0b382b2a227_139594759", "85f8e514-d127-49df-8b2e-76a051ef8d32_25925039", "aea586f4-cbe8-4cc7-82b9-e1b2b6926147_931399657", "d1468c3c-66bf-45f2-aedd-88c6519e1dc3_909172667", "8df408b2-a4b8-4ddf-a1da-96da547a30eb_982545951", "776d6523-b2ce-4640-8969-33bc9666c8d7_71692390", "4a6279a3-1778-4360-aded-589e2a424759_517002533", "bfbd50da-77b8-45