{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1013", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The slow food movement originated in Italy over 30 years ago, focusing on local food and environmental protection.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement was founded by Carlo Petrini to defend regional food traditions and promote sustainable food systems.", "citations": {"96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food movement emphasizes good, clean, and fair food, with over 100,000 members in more than 150 countries.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement promotes inclusivity and equity through initiatives like the Healthy Food for Denver Kids Commission, which annually distributes $12-16 million for food access and education.", "citations": {"11c2142a-10e4-4a59-bf2b-2fd5e48a0f08_553084653": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement promotes cultural heritage, species, and local terroir.", "citations": {"c57552bb-7642-4748-9410-6998d9386d68_512615960": 1.0}}, {"text": "One can visit accredited Slow Food destinations like Taitung, Hualien, or Causeway Coast and Glens to sample the best slow food cuisine.", "citations": {"21597006-6a4b-4e4d-bdb3-16063020492e_526063534": 1.0, "3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 0.5, "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 0.25}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has been adapted in different cultural contexts, such as Hakka cuisine's \"Slow Fast-Food\" concept.", "citations": {"de860988-dbb7-47bb-9919-88ebe56769a3_304327499": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement is also promoted by organizations like Slow Food, which supports quality-focused small businesses and sustainable wineries.", "citations": {"a6e139e5-2201-4127-b6c0-b6b459a4db5e_18544158": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food movement can promote local and traditional food systems while addressing cultural concerns through education and mutual respect.", "citations": {"117ad77e-06c4-477b-a6a9-2822870fe67c_981955395": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement emphasizes seasonality, locality, and tradition to build sustainable communities through local food systems.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has a global presence, with events like the International Slow Food Forum and Earth Markets that support agroecological practices and local economies.", "citations": {"3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363": 1.0, "573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398": 0.5, "b6eb88ba-bab0-4027-b19b-da715a827631_80272630": 0.25}}, {"text": "The movement includes chefs, farmers, and activists like Chef Orkhan Makhtarov, who promote sustainable food systems using locally grown products.", "citations": {"ddc58739-3eff-43d5-908b-9e13da60c3f6_879804265": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food movement aligns with the United Nations' Sustainable Development Goals and promotes sustainable agriculture and preserves traditional food culture.", "citations": {"47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035": 1.0, "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 0.5}}], "references": ["21597006-6a4b-4e4d-bdb3-16063020492e_526063534", "de860988-dbb7-47bb-9919-88ebe56769a3_304327499", "96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237", "c57552bb-7642-4748-9410-6998d9386d68_512615960", "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831", "117ad77e-06c4-477b-a6a9-2822870fe67c_981955395", "573bbdbd-ccb5-417f-82b3-117a2073ed1c_97571398", "a6e139e5-2201-4127-b6c0-b6b459a4db5e_18544158", "47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035", "ddc58739-3eff-43d5-908b-9e13da60c3f6_879804265", "11c2142a-10e4-4a59-bf2b-2fd5e48a0f08_553084653", "3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363", "347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333", "b6eb88ba-bab0-4027-b19b-da715a827631_80272630"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1014", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The slow food movement originated in Italy over 30 years ago, with the goal of defending regional food traditions and promoting sustainable agriculture.", "citations": {"96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement was founded by Carlo Petrini in response to the opening of a McDonald's restaurant in Rome, and has since gained supporters in over 150 countries.", "citations": {"96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food spirit is centered around the principles of \"Good quality, clean and fair\", which emphasize the importance of sustainable and equitable food systems.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement has been promoted globally through events such as the International Slow Food Forum, which has been held in locations such as Taitung, Taiwan.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0}}, {"text": "Taitung has been a hub for slow food activism, with a 10-year history of promoting slow food practices and hosting events such as the Taitung Slow Food Festival.", "citations": {"21597006-6a4b-4e4d-bdb3-16063020492e_526063534": 1.0}}, {"text": "The festival promotes environmental protection and features interactive food promotion booths, as well as discussions on traditional food culture.", "citations": {"7c2a1fe5-6d77-43d3-b615-45dfa7772754_981252650": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has also been recognized internationally, with the Taitung Slow Food Festival winning Japan's Good Design Award.", "citations": {"89e87dc2-272d-4055-8419-f253560719f7_771613945": 1.0}}, {"text": "To sample the best slow food cuisine, one can visit Taitung County in Taiwan, which hosts the Taitung Slow Food Festival, or attend the Terra Madre Salone del Gusto, a global slow food conference.", "citations": {"ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has been driven by various individuals and organizations, including Aruna Tirkey, who founded Oraon Slow Food in Jharkhand, India, and Nazlina Binti Hussin, who founded Nazlina Spice Station in Malaysia.", "citations": {"b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement has also been supported by international organizations, such as the International Slow Food, which has been headed by Andrea Amato, and has regional advisors, such as Ramon Uy Jr, who covers Southeast Asia.", "citations": {"b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the slow food movement has a rich history and has been promoted globally through a variety of events and initiatives, with a focus on sustainability, equity, and accessibility.", "citations": {"96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237": 1.0}}, {"text": "The movement emphasizes the importance of preserving local food cultures and traditions, and has been adapted and implemented in various countries, including Taiwan, India, and Malaysia.", "citations": {"347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has also been recognized for its contributions to promoting sustainable agriculture, reducing the environmental impact of tourism, and supporting local food economies.", "citations": {"47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the movement has also faced criticisms, including high rents that can challenge local food cultures, and competition from larger food businesses that can affect local food economies.", "citations": {"50a413a1-b7c6-46d8-b638-f5a0118367cd_142920352": 1.0}}, {"text": "Despite these challenges, the slow food movement has the potential to promote sustainable agriculture, support local food cultures, and reduce the environmental impact of tourism, but it requires careful consideration of its potential drawbacks and criticisms.", "citations": {"50a413a1-b7c6-46d8-b638-f5a0118367cd_142920352": 1.0}}, {"text": "To mitigate the potential drawbacks of the slow food movement, sustainable and responsible tourism practices can be implemented, such as reducing carbon footprint and supporting local cultures.", "citations": {"e5453a54-a53d-46c1-88ec-cb93130fa116_485767238": 1.0}}, {"text": "Slow travel can also promote local experiences and responsible tourism, reducing travel stress and fatigue.", "citations": {"e5453a54-a53d-46c1-88ec-cb93130fa116_485767238": 1.0}}, {"text": "The slow food movement has been promoted by various governments and organizations, including the Yunlin County government in Taiwan, which has established the Yunlin County International Slow Food Community.", "citations": {"47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035": 1.0}}, {"text": "The community aims to promote high-quality agricultural products and sustainable agriculture practices, while also supporting local food tourism.", "citations": {"47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035": 1.0}}, {"text": "In addition to Taiwan, other locations such as Hualien County have also promoted slow food locally, with a focus on \"high-quality\", \"clean\" and \"fair\" principles.", "citations": {"ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Hualien County Slow Food Team has participated in international Slow Food conferences, promoting the movement's principles and supporting local food cultures.", "citations": {"ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 1.0}}, {"text": "The team has exhibited native seeds and cereals, and launched a cross-border indigenous slow food menu, showcasing the diversity of local cuisine.", "citations": {"ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the slow food movement has the potential to promote sustainable agriculture, support local food cultures, and reduce the environmental impact of tourism, and has been recognized internationally for its contributions to these goals.", "citations": {"96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237": 1.0}}], "references": ["21597006-6a4b-4e4d-bdb3-16063020492e_526063534", "89e87dc2-272d-4055-8419-f253560719f7_771613945", "47c318de-0df6-40ed-976e-0abcd31d8ccb_585421035", "7c2a1fe5-6d77-43d3-b615-45dfa7772754_981252650", "50a413a1-b7c6-46d8-b638-f5a0118367cd_142920352", "ba5e7a01-a860-4e26-a47c-0e52b3c682e6_174285831", "e5453a54-a53d-46c1-88ec-cb93130fa116_485767238", "b702106c-5025-4436-a5d8-8cb8153a683a_482923612", "347aa98a-ba79-4341-963b-fe558f633c81_611052333", "96da40f6-f654-43da-a3f7-d19d9c31ede9_78339237"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1015", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The flat Earth theory is a pseudoscientific idea debated by groups like the Heliopolis Association and the Egyptian Society for Astronomy Sciences.", "citations": {"50c7426a-508b-480c-94f9-7abba543020d_362358128": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flat Earth societies have been criticized by public figures like Richard Dawkins, who urges them to stand up for scientific truth.", "citations": {"4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569": 1.0}}, {"text": "The theory has been promoted by individuals like Kyrie Irving and singer Yuri Loza, who endorsed the flat Earth concept and questioned the validity of space travel.", "citations": {"234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180": 1.0, "2990af1b-c7a6-422c-b322-682c563674ad_197670865": 0.5}}, {"text": "Flat Earth believers include a wide range of individuals, such as NFL players and millennials open to conspiracy theories.", "citations": {"234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180": 1.0, "23b3f452-0d7f-49b9-898d-fa51ce1e5529_717482675": 0.5}}, {"text": "Men tend to believe in socio-political conspiracies, while women tend to believe in food and mysticism conspiracies.", "citations": {"26061d09-b779-4846-8222-ba5ed800e9cb_133337594": 1.0}}, {"text": "Schizotypal and paranoid personality traits, as well as mental disorders, are linked to conspiracy views, including the flat Earth theory.", "citations": {"26061d09-b779-4846-8222-ba5ed800e9cb_133337594": 1.0}}, {"text": "The internet helps spread the flat Earth theory by making confirmatory information easily accessible.", "citations": {"60e14905-14bb-4575-bb8a-a4558a2f1f32_1023504691": 1.0}}, {"text": "Group acceptance motivates flat Earth believers and can lead to cult-like thinking in those seeking simple answers.", "citations": {"60e14905-14bb-4575-bb8a-a4558a2f1f32_1023504691": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flat Earth believers are affected by the Dunning-Kruger effect, a cognitive bias that causes the unqualified to overestimate their knowledge.", "citations": {"615b105e-8676-421b-aea0-b70ed7c4434d_26997891": 1.0}}, {"text": "Isolation, financial difficulties, health issues, narcissism, and a need for uniqueness can increase the likelihood of believing in conspiracy theories like the flat Earth theory.", "citations": {"6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320": 1.0, "bf008ce8-700e-4b3b-88ed-bac465f6aa3b_540286097": 0.5}}, {"text": "Low analytical thinking, high anxiety, security needs, and understanding needs are correlated with conspiracy theory belief.", "citations": {"bf008ce8-700e-4b3b-88ed-bac465f6aa3b_540286097": 1.0}}, {"text": "To address the potential influence of flat Earth theory on teenagers, parents should maintain good communication with their teenagers to discuss the risks of conspiracy theories.", "citations": {"0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184": 1.0}}, {"text": "Getting to know children's friends and monitoring internet use can help parents understand the social influences shaping their teenagers' beliefs and values.", "citations": {"0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184": 1.0}}, {"text": "Showing interest in a teenager's hobbies and needs can help parents build trust and reduce their susceptibility to misinformation.", "citations": {"5b6c419c-56c6-4df3-9cca-e0097a73f5c0_194988493": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parental support reduces adolescent anxiety and suicidal ideation by providing guidance and involvement in their teenagers' lives.", "citations": {"831490cf-a269-4c9f-a2a3-0a9f14a55b56_117367100": 1.0}}], "references": ["26061d09-b779-4846-8222-ba5ed800e9cb_133337594", "4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569", "831490cf-a269-4c9f-a2a3-0a9f14a55b56_117367100", "6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320", "50c7426a-508b-480c-94f9-7abba543020d_362358128", "23b3f452-0d7f-49b9-898d-fa51ce1e5529_717482675", "0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184", "615b105e-8676-421b-aea0-b70ed7c4434d_26997891", "2990af1b-c7a6-422c-b322-682c563674ad_197670865", "5b6c419c-56c6-4df3-9cca-e0097a73f5c0_194988493", "bf008ce8-700e-4b3b-88ed-bac465f6aa3b_540286097", "60e14905-14bb-4575-bb8a-a4558a2f1f32_1023504691", "234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1016", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The flat Earth belief is a complex and multifaceted issue that has gained significant attention in recent years, particularly among certain groups and individuals who promote this idea through various online platforms and social media channels.", "citations": {"234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flat Earth societies and organizations exist in several countries, including the United Kingdom, where universities such as York, Nottingham Trent, and Cambridge have organizations that promote this belief.", "citations": {"4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569": 1.0}}, {"text": "In other countries, such as Egypt, Romania, and Russia, there are also individuals and groups that promote the flat Earth theory, often citing pseudoscientific ideas and conspiracy theories as evidence.", "citations": {"50c7426a-508b-480c-94f9-7abba543020d_362358128": 1.0, "6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320": 0.5, "7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951": 0.25, "ca40ec82-78d0-48df-a54a-d1734fe3a0b3_53647378": 0.125}}, {"text": "Some public figures, including celebrities like Kyrie Irving and Travis Kelce, have also expressed support for the flat Earth theory, which has contributed to its resurgence in popularity.", "citations": {"234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180": 1.0}}, {"text": "The arguments used by flat-earthers to prove their point of view are often based on misconceptions and misinterpretations of scientific evidence, and they frequently cite religious texts and conspiracy theories as evidence.", "citations": {"7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951": 1.0, "1f2e1692-fc89-4d74-94ce-348046c2140b_715798368": 0.5}}, {"text": "The characteristics of people who are most likely to subscribe to flat Earth beliefs are not well-defined, but research suggests that individuals who are vulnerable to conspiracy theories and pseudoscientific ideas may be more susceptible to this belief.", "citations": {"789edb2a-73c1-48a6-b16b-bc09358874f5_454635289": 1.0}}, {"text": "Social media has played a significant role in the spread of flat Earth beliefs, allowing individuals to easily access and share misinformation and conspiracy theories.", "citations": {"23b3f452-0d7f-49b9-898d-fa51ce1e5529_717482675": 1.0}}, {"text": "The lack of critical thinking and media literacy skills can also contribute to the spread of flat Earth beliefs, as individuals may not be able to effectively evaluate the information they encounter online.", "citations": {"789edb2a-73c1-48a6-b16b-bc09358874f5_454635289": 1.0}}, {"text": "To address the issue of flat Earth beliefs, it is essential to focus on education and critical thinking, teaching individuals to evaluate information and make informed decisions.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parents and caregivers can play a crucial role in helping teenagers develop critical thinking skills and make informed decisions about the information they encounter, particularly when it comes to friendships and social relationships.", "citations": {"0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184": 1.0}}, {"text": "By maintaining good communication, setting boundaries, and encouraging critical thinking, parents can help their children navigate complex social relationships and develop resilience.", "citations": {"831490cf-a269-4c9f-a2a3-0a9f14a55b56_117367100": 1.0, "9362ac34-f801-4500-852d-516d4b061738_1061897548": 0.5}}, {"text": "Education and critical thinking are key factors in preventing conspiracy theory beliefs, including flat Earth beliefs, and can help individuals develop the skills to evaluate information and make informed decisions.", "citations": {"0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the flat Earth belief is a complex issue that requires a nuanced and critical approach, taking into account the social, psychological, and cultural factors that contribute to its persistence.", "citations": {"789edb2a-73c1-48a6-b16b-bc09358874f5_454635289": 1.0}}, {"text": "Note: The references provided are based on the doc_id of the source documents.", "citations": {}}], "references": ["ca40ec82-78d0-48df-a54a-d1734fe3a0b3_53647378", "23b3f452-0d7f-49b9-898d-fa51ce1e5529_717482675", "1f2e1692-fc89-4d74-94ce-348046c2140b_715798368", "789edb2a-73c1-48a6-b16b-bc09358874f5_454635289", "831490cf-a269-4c9f-a2a3-0a9f14a55b56_117367100", "4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569", "7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951", "234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180", "9362ac34-f801-4500-852d-516d4b061738_1061897548", "6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320", "50c7426a-508b-480c-94f9-7abba543020d_362358128", "0e11d42f-a5b1-4bbb-b585-84e3274a7239_534772390", "0bccd2ff-59da-4f33-8440-d01ae62047f8_910576184"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1017", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "Disney has been producing live-action remakes of classic animated films like Cinderella, The Jungle Book, and others.", "citations": {"2b7b6721-9b08-432c-b318-1f57bf8a8139_226946838": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's decision to produce remakes is driven by nostalgia, aiming to attract old and new audiences.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes feature big-name stars and advanced technology, as seen in Beauty and the Beast with Emma Watson.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes have achieved commercial success, earning over $1 billion, as seen with Aladdin and The Lion King.", "citations": {"c5f26e63-75b5-48b1-9501-c8ee23be61f2_694539873": 1.0}}, {"text": "The remakes have sparked controversy over casting decisions and changes to original characters and stories.", "citations": {"d8e024e0-ebe0-4e2a-92a9-debca6d24c2e_1011401893": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nostalgia contributes to the backlash against Disney's live-action remakes, which some fans feel do not live up to the originals.", "citations": {"d8e024e0-ebe0-4e2a-92a9-debca6d24c2e_1011401893": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes have altered the original stories, making changes like portraying Snow White as a leader.", "citations": {"577e9503-d0a0-4f40-9ec6-c212b85fd84e_676502879": 1.0}}, {"text": "The remakes feature more realistic and relatable characters, including LGBT ones, as seen in Beauty and the Beast.", "citations": {"7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes of The Little Mermaid and Snow White feature more empowered and independent versions of Ariel and Snow White.", "citations": {"98f59345-0351-4d65-bfc7-7acbaa6eca63_131994914": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes reimagine classic stories for modern audiences while tapping into older audiences' nostalgia.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's remakes, fueled by nostalgia, technology, and big-name stars, have driven box office success, but also sparked controversy and criticism.", "citations": {"6437912b-547a-481e-a130-d37e84d3c639_1009676157": 1.0}}, {"text": "The public reaction to the adaptations has been varied, with some fans appreciating the new takes and others being disappointed by the changes.", "citations": {"9b5bf629-0879-4eaf-9f82-94d4046bbb67_60232712": 1.0}}, {"text": "The success of Disney's live-action remakes depends on balancing nostalgia with modern appeal while staying true to the originals.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney will continue making live-action remakes to evoke nostalgia and attract new audiences.", "citations": {"8a9df4e3-7853-4595-8d6a-57e31dace6a1_812527426": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's approach to live-action remakes will evolve to incorporate audience feedback and modernize original stories and characters.", "citations": {"98f59345-0351-4d65-bfc7-7acbaa6eca63_131994914": 1.0}}], "references": ["6437912b-547a-481e-a130-d37e84d3c639_1009676157", "7f460acf-43fa-4323-886b-7ace4ae531c6_350718074", "8a9df4e3-7853-4595-8d6a-57e31dace6a1_812527426", "98f59345-0351-4d65-bfc7-7acbaa6eca63_131994914", "9b5bf629-0879-4eaf-9f82-94d4046bbb67_60232712", "c5f26e63-75b5-48b1-9501-c8ee23be61f2_694539873", "577e9503-d0a0-4f40-9ec6-c212b85fd84e_676502879", "b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962", "4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830", "2b7b6721-9b08-432c-b318-1f57bf8a8139_226946838", "d8e024e0-ebe0-4e2a-92a9-debca6d24c2e_1011401893"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1018", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "Disney has been producing live-action remakes of classic animated films, including Cinderella, The Jungle Book, and others, to update them for modern audiences.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company produces live-action remakes to capitalize on nostalgia and introduce the stories to new generations.", "citations": {"6cffa8ab-c048-4d6b-9599-de9e62493181_34770675": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nostalgia drives Disney's live-action remakes, aiming to evoke nostalgia in audiences who grew up with the originals.", "citations": {"a46ff8d5-65d2-4767-bbbd-744e15e266f1_655286817": 1.0}}, {"text": "Live-action remakes often feature big-budget productions, update classic stories, and explore new themes, such as villain backstories in Maleficent and Cruella.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes appeal to an older audience due to childhood nostalgia.", "citations": {"c5f26e63-75b5-48b1-9501-c8ee23be61f2_694539873": 1.0}}, {"text": "Childhood nostalgia can lead to backlash over casting decisions, as seen with Halle Bailey's role as Ariel in The Little Mermaid.", "citations": {"8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_769285838": 1.0}}, {"text": "Live-action remakes spark conversation and nostalgia influences fan reaction to casting rumors.", "citations": {"d8e024e0-ebe0-4e2a-92a9-debca6d24c2e_1011401893": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's adaptations teach modern life lessons and values, promoting agency and bravery in young audiences.", "citations": {"d8e024e0-ebe0-4e2a-92a9-debca6d24c2e_1011401893": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's live-action remakes often feature original cast members due to nostalgia.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nostalgia drives fan engagement and high box office performance for Disney's live-action remakes.", "citations": {"6437912b-547a-481e-a130-d37e84d3c639_1009676157": 1.0}}, {"text": "Live-action remakes can still succeed, with fans praising villain roles like Ursula and Captain Hook.", "citations": {"6437912b-547a-481e-a130-d37e84d3c639_1009676157": 1.0}}, {"text": "Not all live-action remakes have been well-received, like Pinocchio, which scored low on Rotten Tomatoes.", "citations": {"a46ff8d5-65d2-4767-bbbd-744e15e266f1_655286817": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Son of Snow White director called Disney's live-action Snow White remake a \"disgrace\" and urged the company to focus on new ideas.", "citations": {"577e9503-d0a0-4f40-9ec6-c212b85fd84e_676502879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney continues to produce live-action remakes, including The Little Mermaid and Snow White.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's approach to updating original stories for modern audiences has been inconsistent, earning both praise and criticism.", "citations": {"9bf4d61e-80c6-417e-8c40-6d987236d4fb_1002818262": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes are criticized for prioritizing diversity and inclusion over storytelling.", "citations": {"04be02f4-bf63-4cf4-a520-2859d5be0752_801436266": 1.0}}, {"text": "The remakes have been criticized for being too similar to the originals and lacking new elements.", "citations": {"577e9503-d0a0-4f40-9ec6-c212b85fd84e_676502879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney continues to produce live-action remakes, including an upcoming version of The Lion King.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's live-action remakes are likely driven by a desire to capitalize on the originals' popularity and update the stories for modern audiences.", "citations": {"2406b73e-b282-4c15-9d39-9f3f821e48a6_195643347": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney aims to evoke nostalgia in audiences while updating the stories for modern times.", "citations": {"2406b73e-b282-4c15-9d39-9f3f821e48a6_195643347": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company balances faithfulness to original stories with updates for contemporary audiences through nostalgia and innovation.", "citations": {"2406b73e-b282-4c15-9d39-9f3f821e48a6_195643347": 1.0}}, {"text": "Public reaction to the adaptations has been mixed, with some embracing the new versions and others preferring the originals.", "citations": {"577e9503-d0a0-4f40-9ec6-c212b85fd84e_676502879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes are driven by nostalgia, innovation, and the desire to update classic stories for contemporary audiences.", "citations": {"2406b73e-b282-4c15-9d39-9f3f821e48a6_195643347": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's ability to balance faithfulness to originals with updates for contemporary audiences will be crucial to their future remakes' success.", "citations": {"2406b73e-b282-4c15-9d39-9f3f821e48a6_195643347": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's Reimagine Tomorrow initiative aims for 50% diverse characters by 2022.", "citations": {"14d044e2-db98-4413-80d5-19f0469ce4c2_251691615": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company consults with diverse communities, like the dwarfism community for the Snow White remake, to ensure respectful and inclusive live-action remakes.", "citations": {"1a1b9fcc-4300-48ca-9dc8-146a2058b715_499911630": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney has reimagined characters in remakes, like the dwarfs in Snow White, to avoid stereotypes.", "citations": {"4d57703a-fc14-4d9b-9892-9d9676d51359_936125144": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company has faced criticism for casting choices, like Halle Bailey as Ariel, but remains committed to diversity and inclusion.", "citations": {"597e8387-d1c3-440e-86e9-f56d0dd63338_585484295": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney is adapting its approach to characters with dwarfism to avoid offense and address representation concerns.", "citations": {"5e5c7575-0fff-41f7-833f-b9ff4b71230c_219533606": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company has cast diverse actors, like Rachel Zegler and Halle Bailey, to make all children feel included.", "citations": {"7807cece-c991-4f8b-9b52-1dcabc779f33_333067711": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney consults with cultural consultants to adapt stories in a respectful and inclusive manner.", "citations": {"838d3eab-afdb-4892-aa3e-b145c7782243_273052995": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's live-action remakes have sparked discussion and controversy over representation and diversity.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action film casting has received polarized reviews for its diversity.", "citations": {"bdddcb95-f6a7-4001-b07d-c74d32a56f6e_1012056560": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney continues to prioritize representation and diversity in its live-action remakes, creating respectful and inclusive content.", "citations": {"bf6f95ae-887b-4ade-b988-4014340d36ba_592417171": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's live-action remakes offer representation to young girls of color and challenge the status quo in fantasy films.", "citations": {"ccab308c-bf61-4f62-8c8b-dc3c493fbed0_494751317": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes have been box office successes, promoting diversity and inclusion while surpassing original earnings.", "citations": {"fff8c0a3-9878-48db-989f-82add6b6c560_882631475": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company showcases its commitment to diversity and inclusion through authentic and respectful content.", "citations": {"fff8c0a3-9878-48db-989f-82add6b6c560_882631475": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney promotes diversity and inclusion through its DEI strategy and donations to organizations like the National Association of Colored People.", "citations": {"bdddcb95-f6a7-4001-b07d-c74d32a56f6e_1012056560": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company has set up a DEI organization and created internal documents to promote diversity and inclusion in its content.", "citations": {"bdddcb95-f6a7-4001-b07d-c74d32a56f6e_1012056560": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes have promoted diversity and inclusion, and the company continues to prioritize representation.", "citations": {"fff8c0a3-9878-48db-989f-82add6b6c560_882631475": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney continues to produce live-action adaptations due to their financial success.", "citations": {"8a9df4e3-7853-4595-8d6a-57e31dace6a1_812527426": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company has adapted beloved animated properties into live-action, including The Little Mermaid.", "citations": {"8a9df4e3-7853-4595-8d6a-57e31dace6a1_812527426": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid live-action remake stars Halle Bailey as Ariel, sparking discussion due to her portrayal of the originally white character.", "citations": {"04527cae-eaa2-4479-bd9d-7e203c3bee3f_435599098": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remake of The Little Mermaid features a darker setting and similar music to the original.", "citations": {"04527cae-eaa2-4479-bd9d-7e203c3bee3f_435599098": 1.0}}, {"text": "Halle Bailey auditioned at 18 and finished filming at 21, a three-year process amidst public pressure and pandemic.", "citations": {"04527cae-eaa2-4479-bd9d-7e203c3bee3f_435599098": 1.0}}, {"text": "The film's trailer was released at the D23 Expo, with Halle Bailey expressing gratitude to the cast on Instagram.", "citations": {"04527cae-eaa2-4479-bd9d-7e203c3bee3f_435599098": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid live-action remake was shot at Pinewood Studios and Sardinia, Italy, with a $250 million budget.", "citations": {"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_814052845": 1.0}}, {"text": "Halle Bailey's performance as Ariel was widely praised, despite the remake receiving mixed reviews from critics.", "citations": {"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_814052845": 1.0}}, {"text": "Rob Marshall, director of The Little Mermaid remake, was moved to tears by Halle Bailey's audition.", "citations": {"1d5975c7-39d8-4a79-bbc2-724d2c6772e0_232560000": 1.0}}, {"text": "The film features beautiful music and sea scenes, with a soundtrack involving Lin-Manuel Miranda.", "citations": {"c71953ee-fe3d-4cbe-b1aa-f035e820bc3a_429435348": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid live-action remake updates Eric, while Ariel's personality remains largely unchanged.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ariel and Eric bond over shared interests in the remake.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}, {"text": "The remake gives Ariel's sisters their own seas and adds motives for Ursula.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action Aladdin remake, starring Mena Massoud and Naomi Scott, owes its success to nostalgia for the original animated classic.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes are often criticized for prioritizing \"political correctness\" over the original story.", "citations": {"9bf4d61e-80c6-417e-8c40-6d987236d4fb_1002818262": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remake approach has been criticized for prioritizing concepts over relatable characters.", "citations": {"9bf4d61e-80c6-417e-8c40-6d987236d4fb_1002818262": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Lion King live-action remake used no actual animals and featured richer character expressions.", "citations": {"9bf4d61e-80c6-417e-8c40-6d987236d4fb_1002818262": 1.0}}, {"text": "Robert Zemeckis' live-action Pinocchio remake scored 27% on Rotten Tomatoes and had a different ending than the original.", "citations": {"a46ff8d5-65d2-4767-bbbd-744e15e266f1_655286817": 1.0}}, {"text": "The film features computer-generated Pinocchio, musical elements, and stars Tom Hanks.", "citations": {"a46ff8d5-65d2-4767-bbbd-744e15e266f1_655286817": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action Beauty remake", "citations": {}}], "references": ["14d044e2-db98-4413-80d5-19f0469ce4c2_251691615", "4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830", "577e9503-d0a0-4f40-9ec6-c212b85fd84e_676502879", "4d57703a-fc14-4d9b-9892-9d9676d51359_936125144", "d8e024e0-ebe0-4e