{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1023", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "Boeing forecasts global demand for 41,170 new aircraft by 2041.", "citations": {"120d7bd4-2830-47f0-a24a-a8deb9c434ff_1037271458": 1.0}}, {"text": "Airlines are demanding new, fuel-efficient aircraft due to growth in air travel.", "citations": {"515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Asia-Pacific region is expected to be the largest market for single-aisle aircraft, with 17,620 new aircraft demanded by 2043.", "citations": {"b7814f2f-30a3-475d-9024-479c2f67817b_166926857": 1.0}}, {"text": "The global single-aisle aircraft market is expected to reach $222.20 billion by 2030, growing at a 12.5% CAGR.", "citations": {"515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685": 1.0}}, {"text": "NASA is developing next-generation aircraft to reduce fuel consumption by 30% by 2030.", "citations": {"b639435f-99b7-479c-9884-7466d11352ba_166330628": 1.0}}, {"text": "The global aviation industry aims to use 30 billion liters of sustainable aviation fuel per year by 2030.", "citations": {"60d24f6f-11c1-4fa7-b01c-19de8707f495_370561689": 1.0}}, {"text": "Demand for SAF is expected to outstrip production due to technological and feedstock limitations.", "citations": {"125fe24b-4acd-4f62-9416-5908a641d534_214878589": 1.0}}, {"text": "The aerospace industry is shifting towards sustainable aviation, with Rolls-Royce's all-electric aircraft having completed its first test flight.", "citations": {"1fc775dc-2141-4589-9133-510fabf35ecb_619044603": 1.0}}, {"text": "Airbus and Boeing expect to sell 43,000 and 39,000 planes, respectively, over the next 20 years.", "citations": {"daae9fd2-8a07-4edc-9903-3bad74d44234_57653713": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Asian market, led by China with a 20% share, is expected to account for 22% of new aircraft deliveries.", "citations": {"65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204": 1.0}}, {"text": "North America and Europe are expected to account for 23% and 17% of new aircraft deliveries, respectively.", "citations": {"5867527f-48e2-4543-921b-79edad641fbf_327309205": 1.0}}, {"text": "From 2022 to 2041, 9,310 aircraft deliveries are predicted in North America.", "citations": {"5264107e-8380-4ecf-8f87-92a0381591f0_64449134": 1.0}}, {"text": "Airbus has a 9.84% market share, surpassing Boeing's 4.02%.", "citations": {"c42332c2-1492-4fbd-978b-4b108988d734_686742304": 1.0}}, {"text": "Airbus led the jet-maker industry for the third consecutive year, delivering 611 aircraft, an 8% increase from the previous year.", "citations": {"424eec40-2248-478f-a963-2162b3850e71_136284801": 1.0}}, {"text": "Boeing received 909 orders last year, surpassing Airbus' 771, with the 737 Max being its main delivery aircraft.", "citations": {"424eec40-2248-478f-a963-2162b3850e71_136284801": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sustainable aviation fuels and electric propulsion systems are expected to impact aircraft manufacturers' return on investment.", "citations": {"00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sustainable aviation fuel can reduce greenhouse gas emissions by 80% compared to conventional jet fuel.", "citations": {"833892cf-f345-4674-a75c-52170bad7e90_405374091": 1.0, "c9661a22-a3c1-4368-9048-0de5b2d6603f_611179": 0.5}}, {"text": "The EU aims to reduce aviation CO2 emissions by 5% by 2030.", "citations": {"4935bc39-e6ed-4768-bba2-f2789433cf19_414528207": 1.0, "c9661a22-a3c1-4368-9048-0de5b2d6603f_611179": 0.5}}, {"text": "Airbus' ZEROe concept aircraft, powered by hydrogen, is expected to enter service by 2035.", "citations": {"5d5a3096-4c80-424f-96cd-6e72bf6f6fbe_986621407": 1.0, "cf58e6c6-c3e8-485d-b30a-70689cba1777_453558165": 0.5}}, {"text": "Airbus aims for 100% sustainable aviation fuel flight certification by 2030 through an agreement with China Aviation Fuel Group.", "citations": {"4ac954af-3e84-4da7-be8e-d8bb4ae2ea74_757059073": 1.0}}], "references": ["00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700", "c9661a22-a3c1-4368-9048-0de5b2d6603f_611179", "c42332c2-1492-4fbd-978b-4b108988d734_686742304", "cf58e6c6-c3e8-485d-b30a-70689cba1777_453558165", "1fc775dc-2141-4589-9133-510fabf35ecb_619044603", "b639435f-99b7-479c-9884-7466d11352ba_166330628", "4935bc39-e6ed-4768-bba2-f2789433cf19_414528207", "424eec40-2248-478f-a963-2162b3850e71_136284801", "515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685", "125fe24b-4acd-4f62-9416-5908a641d534_214878589", "4ac954af-3e84-4da7-be8e-d8bb4ae2ea74_757059073", "5867527f-48e2-4543-921b-79edad641fbf_327309205", "daae9fd2-8a07-4edc-9903-3bad74d44234_57653713", "120d7bd4-2830-47f0-a24a-a8deb9c434ff_1037271458", "65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204", "b7814f2f-30a3-475d-9024-479c2f67817b_166926857", "60d24f6f-11c1-4fa7-b01c-19de8707f495_370561689", "5264107e-8380-4ecf-8f87-92a0381591f0_64449134", "5d5a3096-4c80-424f-96cd-6e72bf6f6fbe_986621407", "833892cf-f345-4674-a75c-52170bad7e90_405374091"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1024", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The global aerospace industry is shifting towards greater efficiency and sustainability, driven by the need to reduce carbon emissions and meet increasing demand for air travel, with emerging technologies such as advanced materials and digitalization expected to play a crucial role in the development of innovative propulsion systems and sustainable aviation fuels.", "citations": {"f3b24342-5671-4d85-a812-56608e542295_86608218": 1.0}}, {"text": "The demand for new aircraft is expected to reach 43,610 in 20 years, with North America having the highest demand at 9,160 aircraft, and the Asia-Pacific region expected to exhibit the highest CAGR in the aerospace foam market, driven by increasing air travelers.", "citations": {"bf2732d0-bb7b-4e55-9d35-f1d548672746_296106203": 1.0, "58cb9ae7-c967-4d94-9059-9765953b9d81_31367334": 0.5}}, {"text": "Boeing expects 44,000 aircraft to be needed by 2043, with the total number of planes in use almost doubling by 2043, and the demand for new aircraft is increasing due to replacement and bottlenecks, with the fleet age being one to one-and-a-half years older.", "citations": {"2ff4c61a-59c1-406b-a506-d4c10f66932f_241818403": 1.0}}, {"text": "The single-aisle aircraft market will require 26.73 thousand aircraft, with the wide-body segment requiring 8.83 thousand new aircraft, and passenger traffic is expected to grow at 5% per year, with air freight volume growing 4.7% annually.", "citations": {"35bf81d9-8fb4-4f64-9478-54e28df42730_900060412": 1.0}}, {"text": "The total value of new aircraft is estimated to be $5.6 trillion, with 45,000 fuel-efficient aircraft expected to be delivered by 2040, and the global civil aviation fleet will surpass 49,000 by 2040, with Asia Pacific, Europe, and North America accounting for 80% of global demand.", "citations": {"bf2732d0-bb7b-4e55-9d35-f1d548672746_296106203": 1.0, "65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204": 0.5}}, {"text": "The key trends driving growth in the aerospace market towards sustainability include the growing demand for commercial aircraft in developing nations, increasing airline passenger traffic, and the need for sustainable and high-performance aerospace components.", "citations": {"011e96af-2bff-45dd-89ba-29f71b7989f2_783464216": 1.0}}, {"text": "The development of hydrogen-powered aircraft is a key area of focus for the aviation industry, with companies such as Rolls-Royce and easyJet testing hydrogen jet engines for aircraft use, and Airbus planning to test hydrogen engines on an A380 by 2026.", "citations": {"15f6df22-73de-4965-8ffe-9d62c4f496c6_164078516": 1.0, "8733e1f4-7bde-4373-8a02-93cf091bf450_924345843": 0.5}}, {"text": "The implementation of sustainable aviation fuels (SAFs) is expected to play a significant role in reducing carbon emissions in the aviation industry, with some estimates suggesting that SAFs could account for up to 5% of global jet fuel demand by 2030.", "citations": {"125fe24b-4acd-4f62-9416-5908a641d534_214878589": 1.0}}, {"text": "The global sustainable aviation fuel market is expected to reach $2987.5 million by 2027, driven by the rising need to reduce GHG emissions and high fuel efficiency of sustainable aviation fuel, with North America expected to serve as a lucrative growth avenue for sustainable aviation fuel.", "citations": {"15dbbde3-8146-4ee0-b763-10d0733a16bc_355311255": 1.0}}, {"text": "The integration of electric-hybrid propulsion systems into commercial aircraft is a promising area of development, with key concerns including reliability and safety of operation, as well as economic aspects, and the Global Hybrid Electric Jet market was valued at millions in 2021 and is projected to reach millions by 2028.", "citations": {"00580580-2d22-4655-a113-539c80fc105d_1072121227": 1.0, "00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700": 0.5}}, {"text": "The adoption of sustainable aviation fuels and innovative propulsion systems is supported by various regulatory and policy frameworks globally, with countries such as Japan aiming for net zero greenhouse gas emissions by 2050, and the International Civil Aviation Organization (ICAO) promoting sustainable fuel technology to reduce CO2 emissions.", "citations": {"0d53ed59-7097-439d-992f-d7a9e153837c_597630051": 1.0, "513ef66e-085a-4865-9d81-62e5b51b62e4_491272360": 0.5}}, {"text": "Overall, the aerospace industry is expected to experience significant growth in the next two decades, driven by increasing demand for air travel and the need for sustainable and efficient aircraft, with emerging technologies such as advanced materials, digitalization, and sustainable aviation fuels expected to play a crucial role in shaping the future of the industry.", "citations": {"f3b24342-5671-4d85-a812-56608e542295_86608218": 1.0}}], "references": ["011e96af-2bff-45dd-89ba-29f71b7989f2_783464216", "8733e1f4-7bde-4373-8a02-93cf091bf450_924345843", "125fe24b-4acd-4f62-9416-5908a641d534_214878589", "00ac3a93-3310-4f70-9268-f04353c61fc3_623414700", "35bf81d9-8fb4-4f64-9478-54e28df42730_900060412", "15dbbde3-8146-4ee0-b763-10d0733a16bc_355311255", "bf2732d0-bb7b-4e55-9d35-f1d548672746_296106203", "00580580-2d22-4655-a113-539c80fc105d_1072121227", "f3b24342-5671-4d85-a812-56608e542295_86608218", "2ff4c61a-59c1-406b-a506-d4c10f66932f_241818403", "0d53ed59-7097-439d-992f-d7a9e153837c_597630051", "513ef66e-085a-4865-9d81-62e5b51b62e4_491272360", "65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204", "58cb9ae7-c967-4d94-9059-9765953b9d81_31367334", "15f6df22-73de-4965-8ffe-9d62c4f496c6_164078516"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1025", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The construction industry is becoming more balanced, with female participation increasing over the past decade.", "citations": {"185c412e-f5be-452c-9b08-11c17a652d52_115437239": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are increasingly participating in male-dominated industries, such as construction in China.", "citations": {"4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_966556193": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry is expected to increase inclusivity for women through improved PPE and safety.", "citations": {"539767b2-3f00-49ee-b52b-9964067b245c_208662540": 1.0}}, {"text": "US women in construction have reached 14.1 percent, totaling 440,000 jobs, the highest since 2001.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "A quarter of female workers have experienced on-site sexual harassment, and half have faced unequal treatment from men.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women made up 14% of China's construction workforce by 2018.", "citations": {"5d510a0c-546d-4abc-b754-de4153cf36ae_716225683": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women comprise 16% of the construction workforce and 4% of site managers.", "citations": {"810dbd83-66fd-46d5-b733-7fd200ef200c_901656784": 1.0}}, {"text": "The homebuilding industry is encouraging women into site management through programs addressing gender imbalance.", "citations": {"810dbd83-66fd-46d5-b733-7fd200ef200c_901656784": 1.0}}, {"text": "Elena Badaeva, a female crane operator since 1989, broke traditional gender barriers operating at about 40 meters altitude.", "citations": {"14d2b2e8-59cd-4d3e-ab35-cf57fee10e78_86706736": 1.0}}, {"text": "Loretta Barnett is a second-generation female crane operator at Savannah River Site.", "citations": {"3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997": 1.0}}, {"text": "Farkhana Safargaleeva, a dedicated female crane operator, has 15 years of construction experience, with a 5-year hiatus.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hsing and Shan, a mother-daughter duo, are female crane operators in Hong Kong's construction industry, breaking traditional gender barriers.", "citations": {"d1cbc72f-fc5b-4e32-92e9-426811b18a66_339041828": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women like Elena Badaeva and others have broken down traditional gender barriers in construction, particularly in crane operation.", "citations": {"14d2b2e8-59cd-4d3e-ab35-cf57fee10e78_86706736": 1.0, "3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997": 0.5, "485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 0.25, "d1cbc72f-fc5b-4e32-92e9-426811b18a66_339041828": 0.125}}, {"text": "The WANTT non-profit organization helps women enter the construction industry by offering pre-apprenticeship programs.", "citations": {"1c945363-358c-4398-9ccb-11aac43f6ef2_118306949": 1.0}}, {"text": "Illinois has received $1 million to promote women in construction, with the Chicago Women in Trades organization receiving grant money.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE has launched the \"Leaders in Difference\" initiative to empower women in the maritime sector.", "citations": {"446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hard work and determination are crucial for women to break into male-dominated fields like crane operation.", "citations": {"bf6c1f9b-f19a-4c11-991c-650da7e72cf2_1069158876": 1.0}}, {"text": "Trade union support can help women enter industries and secure equal pay for equal work.", "citations": {"bf6c1f9b-f19a-4c11-991c-650da7e72cf2_1069158876": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women in crane operation can overcome physical strength challenges with proper training and mindset.", "citations": {"bf6c1f9b-f19a-4c11-991c-650da7e72cf2_1069158876": 1.0}}], "references": ["bf6c1f9b-f19a-4c11-991c-650da7e72cf2_1069158876", "3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997", "1c945363-358c-4398-9ccb-11aac43f6ef2_118306949", "d1cbc72f-fc5b-4e32-92e9-426811b18a66_339041828", "5d510a0c-546d-4abc-b754-de4153cf36ae_716225683", "3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734", "14d2b2e8-59cd-4d3e-ab35-cf57fee10e78_86706736", "485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500", "539767b2-3f00-49ee-b52b-9964067b245c_208662540", "810dbd83-66fd-46d5-b733-7fd200ef200c_901656784", "4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_966556193", "446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030", "185c412e-f5be-452c-9b08-11c17a652d52_115437239", "589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1026", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The construction and maritime industries have traditionally been male-dominated, but there is a growing trend towards greater gender equality and diversity, with women increasingly taking on roles such as crane operators.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are breaking down traditional gender barriers in the construction and maritime industries by taking on roles such as crane operators, a field that has historically been dominated by men.", "citations": {"3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE has launched initiatives such as \"Leaders in Difference\" to empower women in the maritime sector, prioritizing female talent in maritime workforce development and aiming to recruit diverse talent for sector growth.", "citations": {"446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can promote diversity and inclusion by implementing flexible work arrangements, such as flexible working hours and locations, to support employees with family care needs.", "citations": {"0e076a21-8cb1-417d-b7b7-30ff249870ed_940326048": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Maritime Employee Survey tracks employment trends and diversity initiatives, providing insights into progress on tackling workplace discrimination and allowing employers to understand workforce experiences.", "citations": {"07631742-4202-4035-a1b6-b234f8adbed3_328786045": 1.0}}, {"text": "To support the retention and advancement of female crane operators, employers should provide flexible working hours and arrangements, such as extended maternity leave and parental leave, to help them balance work and family responsibilities.", "citations": {"0e076a21-8cb1-417d-b7b7-30ff249870ed_940326048": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators require specific technical skills and training, including knowledge of physics and geometry, as well as certifications such as NCCCO certification and 06102 Fixed Crane Operation.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0, "ab8df9e5-b36b-4dd7-8673-9fa067add4c1_1053223185": 0.5, "b6fb4342-3bba-47b7-852a-325e7aa4f3f6_1007863897": 0.25}}, {"text": "Companies can design and implement effective training programs for female crane operators by utilizing technology for on-the-job training, such as virtual reality simulation, and providing mentorship programs and on-the-job coaching.", "citations": {"28923813-55c8-41ac-8db1-7e780c2db2b9_323149195": 1.0, "53ec3f8b-1f33-4db7-b460-fc0533d8e9db_312525721": 0.5, "86cbd746-91e5-4583-a65d-05c1f8904f44_169456569": 0.25, "87389b22-7dba-4886-94a2-dde178f4d5e7_437212916": 0.125, "9b95a346-03b3-49ba-86e4-adf7e644b438_910039464": 0.0625, "b2bc80ec-0613-4159-9f01-4364946e0cf0_738860149": 0.03125, "bbfe37ef-d0b1-45c7-b8e1-3671ef1d1c09_938199491": 0.015625, "bcda4cee-ba76-4966-8dc6-1bfea85b5870_708941358": 0.0078125, "c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 0.00390625}}, {"text": "The use of virtual reality simulators can provide a hyperrealistic and immersive training experience for crane operators, increasing their professional level and reducing the risk of accidents.", "citations": {"bcda4cee-ba76-4966-8dc6-1bfea85b5870_708941358": 1.0}}, {"text": "Leadership support is essential for successful diversity, equity, and inclusion practices, and having women in decision-making forums can prevent exceptional treatment.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regular feedback mechanisms and monitoring changes in perceptions can help prevent disparities and support better company culture.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can measure the effectiveness of their diversity and inclusion initiatives by tracking employment trends, monitoring changes in perceptions, and analyzing data on pay gaps.", "citations": {"07631742-4202-4035-a1b6-b234f8adbed3_328786045": 1.0, "59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 0.5, "980697fc-65d2-4a9e-b57c-9fc46559ec33_512741972": 0.25}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organization launched the International Day for Women in Maritime to support industry diversity and inclusivity.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women's networks are being created in historically conservative organizations, and shipping companies are incentivizing gender diversity through loan agreements.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the construction and maritime industries are making progress towards greater gender equality and diversity, with a growing number of women taking on roles such as crane operators and companies implementing initiatives to support their retention and advancement.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}], "references": ["bcda4cee-ba76-4966-8dc6-1bfea85b5870_708941358", "485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500", "c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220", "f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554", "b6fb4342-3bba-47b7-852a-325e7aa4f3f6_1007863897", "53ec3f8b-1f33-4db7-b460-fc0533d8e9db_312525721", "87389b22-7dba-4886-94a2-dde178f4d5e7_437212916", "59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573", "28923813-55c8-41ac-8db1-7e780c2db2b9_323149195", "980697fc-65d2-4a9e-b57c-9fc46559ec33_512741972", "07631742-4202-4035-a1b6-b234f8adbed3_328786045", "bbfe37ef-d0b1-45c7-b8e1-3671ef1d1c09_938199491", "86cbd746-91e5-4583-a65d-05c1f8904f44_169456569", "9b95a346-03b3-49ba-86e4-adf7e644b438_910039464", "446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030", "3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997", "b2bc80ec-0613-4159-9f01-4364946e0cf0_738860149", "0e076a21-8cb1-417d-b7b7-30ff249870ed_940326048", "ab8df9e5-b36b-4dd7-8673-9fa067add4c1_1053223185"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1027", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "To attract women construction workers, especially those operating heavy machinery, the company must understand the shift towards greater gender equality in the industry.", "citations": {}}, {"text": "The construction industry is becoming more balanced, with women bringing unique skills like empathy and organizational abilities as the number of female engineers increases.", "citations": {"185c412e-f5be-452c-9b08-11c17a652d52_115437239": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women still face challenges in male-dominated industries, including bias, skepticism, and unfair treatment.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can address challenges by providing training, mentorship, and a supportive work environment that promotes diversity and inclusion.", "citations": {"78aea070-dd24-4942-b36f-18695f08e7f2_921333581": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can access technical training on heavy equipment operation, including crane operation, and companies offer supporting certifications and training programs.", "citations": {"11ab6d68-4519-4f35-a03c-b936a76014bc_273648372": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mentorship programs can help women build confidence and skills, especially in non-traditional roles.", "citations": {"08ca1907-7f61-4ff5-bf33-c80a91a3c5d7_971189628": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diverse teams drive innovation and business success, and creating an inclusive culture that supports working mothers is essential for above-average earnings.", "citations": {"0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can promote diversity and inclusion in construction by supporting women in non-traditional roles.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "Empowering women in the workforce can lead to economic growth, staff stability, and increased innovation through diversity and inclu