{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1029", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The science fiction genre has evolved over time, shaped by pioneers like H.G. Wells and Mary Shelley.", "citations": {"3d319f9a-69dd-4ae0-aa70-9a2ebdc0bdea_174201959": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre explores threats like nuclear power, racism, and environmental issues, influenced by ideologies such as capitalism and communism.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "Science fiction reflects modern themes like transhumanism and artificial intelligence in authors such as Isaac Asimov and Arthur C. Clarke.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has branched into sub-genres like hard sci-fi, dystopian, and cyberpunk, with notable authors including William Gibson and Ursula K. Le Guin.", "citations": {"8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women authors like Mary Shelley and Ursula K. Le Guin have significantly impacted science fiction, challenging traditional gender and identity notions.", "citations": {"774699db-8b63-4839-8211-2760098d90ac_1033840002": 1.0}}, {"text": "Authors of color, such as Cixin Liu and Nnedi Okorafor, have gained international recognition for their unique science fiction perspectives.", "citations": {"8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction genre has become more diverse, exploring a wide range of themes and incorporating new ideas.", "citations": {"925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162": 1.0}}, {"text": "A book club reading list should balance classic and contemporary science fiction by including diverse authors like Kazuo Ishiguro and Ursula K. Le Guin.", "citations": {"925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Hugo Award is a useful reading guide for science fiction, helping book clubs discover new authors and diverse perspectives.", "citations": {"1af7c5c0-2cd8-4ccb-ae8a-3d495406430b_509519304": 1.0}}, {"text": "Notable authors like Neil Gaiman and Ursula Le Guin, who have won Hugo Awards, are great options for book club selections.", "citations": {"1af7c5c0-2cd8-4ccb-ae8a-3d495406430b_509519304": 1.0}}, {"text": "Liu Cixin, a Chinese science fiction writer, won the Hugo Award for Best Novel in 2015.", "citations": {"6a242539-f0c5-48d1-90a3-3e492490b2ab_968075804": 1.0}}, {"text": "When evaluating science fiction books, consider allegories, world-building, character development, and moral dilemmas.", "citations": {"8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The book should appeal to diverse backgrounds and be accessible to a wide range of readers.", "citations": {"a25fc9b0-47f1-40b3-ae2b-abbd0671f8ec_931795328": 1.0}}, {"text": "The goal is to choose a book that will generate interesting discussions and provide a thought-provoking reading experience.", "citations": {"babbd892-aaae-47c2-814d-61139b3086eb_802108510": 1.0}}, {"text": "Science fiction has been influenced by authors from diverse demographics, including women and people of color.", "citations": {"65d33e53-1e25-496f-bafa-89b8fb4b7589_329943394": 1.0}}], "references": ["925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162", "6a242539-f0c5-48d1-90a3-3e492490b2ab_968075804", "8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018", "3d319f9a-69dd-4ae0-aa70-9a2ebdc0bdea_174201959", "774699db-8b63-4839-8211-2760098d90ac_1033840002", "babbd892-aaae-47c2-814d-61139b3086eb_802108510", "01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677", "1af7c5c0-2cd8-4ccb-ae8a-3d495406430b_509519304", "65d33e53-1e25-496f-bafa-89b8fb4b7589_329943394", "a25fc9b0-47f1-40b3-ae2b-abbd0671f8ec_931795328"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1030", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The evolution of science fiction literature has been influenced by various ideologies, including capitalism and communism, as well as concerns about nuclear power, racism, ecological crises, and climate change.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has been shaped by literary prizes, which have influenced the development of science fiction, and has included works from diverse geographical and linguistic fields.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "Semiotics and feminist studies have been used to analyze science fiction narratives, while anthropology and postcolonial studies have informed science fiction perspectives.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Hugo Award is the highest honor in contemporary science fiction, and was named after Gensbach's contributions in 1955, becoming the official name in 1958.", "citations": {"1af7c5c0-2cd8-4ccb-ae8a-3d495406430b_509519304": 1.0}}, {"text": "Notable science fiction authors have won the Hugo Award, including Jo Walton, who won the 2012 Hugo Award for fiction, and Chiang Feng-nan, who won four Hugo Awards between 2002 and 2011.", "citations": {"1af7c5c0-2cd8-4ccb-ae8a-3d495406430b_509519304": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has also been influenced by authors from diverse demographics, including women authors and people of color, who have made significant contributions to the genre.", "citations": {"764901a5-ae9e-4bb0-be99-00e9fcaa1a8b_389925305": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ahmed Saadawi wrote \"Frankenstein in Baghdad\", a novel that explores the intersection of science fiction and Middle Eastern culture.", "citations": {"764901a5-ae9e-4bb0-be99-00e9fcaa1a8b_389925305": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Handmaid's Tale by Margaret Atwood is a classic dystopian novel that explores themes of feminism and oppression.", "citations": {"8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Three-Body Problem by Cixin Liu is a new epic involving alien invasion and moral dilemmas, and has won numerous awards for its unique blend of science fiction and Chinese culture.", "citations": {"8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018": 1.0}}, {"text": "Contemporary science fiction authors from underrepresented perspectives, such as women and people of color, are subverting traditional science fiction tropes and themes, and this is having a significant impact on the genre as a whole.", "citations": {"925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162": 1.0}}, {"text": "The rise of Chinese science fiction has also led to an increase in diverse authors, with Chinese female writers like Regina Kanyu Wang being nominated for Hugo Awards and four anthologies of Chinese fantasy novels by female authors being published.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The internet has also played a significant role in helping women and queer talents in writing science fiction, with online platforms and communities providing opportunities for authors to share their work and connect with readers.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the genre of science fiction has evolved significantly over time, with contributions from diverse authors and demographics, and continues to be shaped by new and innovative voices.", "citations": {"8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has become more diverse, with authors from various demographics, such as women and people of color, making an impact and contributing to the evolution of science fiction.", "citations": {"521ac676-eb0a-4808-8618-33cf0a1f7330_242685488": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of emerging technologies like AI and VR is changing the way authors write and publish science fiction, and new opportunities and challenges are emerging as a result.", "citations": {"7449fc8d-a2fb-4f79-848e-4d7faf561792_254013990": 1.0}}, {"text": "Authors must consider the potential benefits and drawbacks of using AI and VR in their work, and must be aware of the potential for these technologies to replace certain aspects of the writing process.", "citations": {"ba386436-9abc-40df-885a-ebae78c6124c_796301023": 1.0}}, {"text": "The incorporation of emerging technologies into science fiction is not without its challenges, and authors must be willing to adapt and evolve in order to succeed.", "citations": {"d13e812c-5ede-4af9-a365-fd13741bc596_1029488381": 1.0}}, {"text": "Despite the challenges, the use of emerging technologies like AI and VR is opening up new opportunities for science fiction authors and is allowing them to explore new themes and ideas.", "citations": {"7e419fc1-0a90-48de-90ec-e777cf646241_187716990": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction genre has undergone significant changes and evolution over time, with various factors influencing its development, including social and cultural shifts.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Online platforms and social media have played a crucial role in promoting diversity and inclusivity in the science fiction genre, providing a space for underrepresented authors to connect with readers and share their work.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The internet has removed barriers to writing for non-male authors, allowing them to overcome industry barriers and thrive in the science fiction genre.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chinese female writers, in particular, have made significant contributions to the genre, focusing on issues unique to female experiences and publishing numerous anthologies of fantasy novels.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The rise of online platforms has also led to an increase in women writers in science fiction, with Chinese science fiction readers now split equally between men and women.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Social media has helped authors from underrepresented backgrounds connect with readers, promoting diversity and inclusivity in the genre.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "African writers have also benefited from online platforms, which have provided a space for emerging voices and supported many African writers, particularly those from the LGBTQ+ community.", "citations": {"72484329-e5c6-4529-8160-0e99e3ceec2d_513234228": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction genre continues to evolve, with new authors and voices emerging, and the influence of authors like Okorafor and Liu can be seen in the growing diversity of the genre.", "citations": {"06063c28-5fa9-4c36-bdf3-33e5e9465ef6_990466040": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reception of works by authors from diverse backgrounds has been largely positive, with critics and audiences praising their unique perspectives and innovative storytelling.", "citations": {"06063c28-5fa9-4c36-bdf3-33e5e9465ef6_990466040": 1.0}}, {"text": "The impact of authors from other demographics, such as women authors and people of color, has been significant, bringing new ideas and perspectives to the genre.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction genre has evolved over time, with earlier authors like HG Wells influencing the development of the genre, and modern authors incorporating new technologies and ideas into their work.", "citations": {"7e419fc1-0a90-48de-90ec-e777cf646241_187716990": 1.0}}, {"text": "Emerging technologies like AI and VR are providing new opportunities for science fiction authors to explore the human impact of technological advancements.", "citations": {"7e419fc1-0a90-48de-90ec-e777cf646241_187716990": 1.0}}, {"text": "Authors are using science fiction to explore human concerns and emotions, and to comment on the potential risks and benefits of emerging technologies.", "citations": {"7e419fc1-0a90-48de-90ec-e777cf646241_187716990": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of AI and VR in science fiction is not without its challenges, but authors are finding new and innovative ways to incorporate these technologies into their work.", "citations": {"dff8c664-54dc-4149-9533-08368152a7d5_403909761": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Hugo Award is considered the most important literary award in science fiction, and it is chosen by science fiction fans' votes, which helps drive readers' interest in science fiction reading.", "citations": {"1af7c5c0-2cd8-4ccb-ae8a-3d495406430b_509519304": 1.0}}, {"text": "The award is used as a reading guide for science fiction and has helped to re-popularize classic science fiction works through film adaptations.", "citations": {"1af7c5c0-2cd8-4ccb-ae8a-3d495406430b_509519304": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction industry in China has reached 87.75 billion yuan in revenue in 2022 and is still developing, with new technologies expanding the space for science fiction creation.", "citations": {"abaa0015-a46d-424f-9c06-e6df34a0b588_865359249": 1.0}}, {"text": "Online platforms and social media have also posed challenges for authors, including the potential for the squandering of writers' rights and the need for authors to adapt to new publishing windows.", "citations": {"7e419fc1-0a90-48de-90ec-e777cf646241_920113411": 1.0}}, {"text": "Despite these challenges, online platforms have provided opportunities for new writers to publish their work and for authors to display their creative production freely and widely.", "citations": {"7e419fc1-0a90-48de-90ec-e777cf646241_920113411": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of social media has also led to the adaptation of online novels into movies and TV series, increasing their value and attraction.", "citations": {"dd110cfe-1623-4ad9-8ac9-8824567e1742_194170105": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, dialogue presentation and rhythm and pacing are major challenges when adapting online novels into different mediums.", "citations": {"dd110cfe-1623-4ad9-8ac9-8824567e1742_194170105": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, online platforms and social media have had a significant impact on the science fiction genre, presenting both opportunities and challenges for authors from underrepresented backgrounds.", "citations": {"21bf354d-f8ba-4002-a234-4dec5f8b44d4_685175235": 1.0}}], "references": ["06063c28-5fa9-4c36-bdf3-33e5e9465ef6_990466040", "40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979", "521ac676-eb0a-4808-8618-33cf0a1f7330_242685488", "dd110cfe-1623-4ad9-8ac9-8824567e1742_194170105", "7e419fc1-0a90-48de-90ec-e777cf646241_920113411", "925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162", "abaa0015-a46d-424f-9c06-e6df34a0b588_865359249", "8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018", "1af7c5c0-2cd8-4ccb-ae8a-3d495406430b_509519304", "7449fc8d-a2fb-4f79-848e-4d7faf561792_254013990", "ba386436-9abc-40df-885a-ebae78c6124c_796301023", "7e419fc1-0a90-48de-90ec-e777cf646241_187716990", "01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677", "dff8c664-54dc-4149-9533-08368152a7d5_403909761", "d13e812c-5ede-4af9-a365-fd13741bc596_1029488381", "21bf354d-f8ba-4002-a234-4dec5f8b44d4_685175235", "72484329-e5c6-4529-8160-0e99e3ceec2d_513234228", "764901a5-ae9e-4bb0-be99-00e9fcaa1a8b_389925305"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1031", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "Africa's foreign direct investment reached $1.65 trillion in 2021, a 77% increase from 2020.", "citations": {"23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891": 1.0}}, {"text": "The continent offers competitive opportunities for investors, with African markets having the highest global return on investment.", "citations": {"49df26a7-82a0-4dc1-bb11-c6e257cf429b_167847908": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investment in Africa is expected to focus on sustainable infrastructure, such as the Just Energy Transition Partnership to decarbonize South Africa's economy.", "citations": {"12d9d4c8-91d8-4490-a011-119a8e01ecfc_380777410": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt's economy grew 6.6% in 2021/2022 and 4.4% in Q1 2023, with foreign direct investment expected to reach $16.5 billion by 2025.", "citations": {"77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447": 1.0}}, {"text": "The African Continental Free Trade Area (AfCFTA) aims to create a single market of 1.3 billion people with a $3.4 trillion GDP.", "citations": {"a948934f-cc3e-4b6b-ba17-7748e34ef2c6_397268782": 1.0}}, {"text": "A $20 billion wind energy project in Morocco, backed by major foreign companies, aims to export energy to the UK.", "citations": {"da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investment in Africa has focused on regions like North, West, and East Africa, with countries such as Egypt, South Africa, and Nigeria being major recipients.", "citations": {"695fcb24-fc0c-4dc2-8d8a-4daca5fdf475_215879209": 1.0}}, {"text": "Industrial areas with significant foreign investment include infrastructure, mining, finance, renewable energy, agriculture, and tourism.", "citations": {"582b94f4-8a99-4e02-baa9-ddade643f876_420424382": 1.0}}, {"text": "Major foreign companies like Google, Microsoft, and Coca-Cola have invested in Africa, often in partnership with local entities like the African Development Bank and the Egyptian government.", "citations": {"12d9d4c8-91d8-4490-a011-119a8e01ecfc_380777410": 1.0, "6345d4b8-fb97-4192-87f0-120c360175a2_822988963": 0.5}}, {"text": "Africa's projected foreign investment is significant, with $16.12 trillion in consumer spending expected by 2050.", "citations": {"a948934f-cc3e-4b6b-ba17-7748e34ef2c6_397268782": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investment in Africa can drive economic growth, but it must be managed to minimize negative social and environmental impacts.", "citations": {"d17ecd8a-4688-40cf-a754-b16711db9af1_281469657": 1.0}}, {"text": "Public-private partnerships play a crucial role in Africa's economic growth, implementing infrastructure projects and bridging budget gaps.", "citations": {"09ef5f7e-f47e-4b8e-b301-c32e10823525_96128367": 1.0}}, {"text": "Addressing challenges like energy deficits, corruption, and regulatory uncertainties is essential to unlock Africa's full potential.", "citations": {"ea26aacb-88c6-4f9b-b777-714b3d73909e_932614160": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa is expected to continue attracting foreign investment due to its large market, rich resources, and improving business climate.", "citations": {"a948934f-cc3e-4b6b-ba17-7748e34ef2c6_397268782": 1.0}}], "references": ["49df26a7-82a0-4dc1-bb11-c6e257cf429b_167847908", "a948934f-cc3e-4b6b-ba17-7748e34ef2c6_397268782", "582b94f4-8a99-4e02-baa9-ddade643f876_420424382", "77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447", "695fcb24-fc0c-4dc2-8d8a-4daca5fdf475_215879209", "6345d4b8-fb97-4192-87f0-120c360175a2_822988963", "09ef5f7e-f47e-4b8e-b301-c32e10823525_96128367", "23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891", "ea26aacb-88c6-4f9b-b777-714b3d73909e_932614160", "da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125", "d17ecd8a-4688-40cf-a754-b16711db9af1_281469657", "12d9d4c8-91d8-4490-a011-119a8e01ecfc_380777410"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1032", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "Africa's foreign direct investment (FDI) reached a record $1.65 trillion in 2021, up 77% from 2020.", "citations": {"23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa is a top investment destination, with Egypt being the largest, boasting an 8% growth rate.", "citations": {"2d53bcf5-e733-4209-8d61-53b587b8bc19_796995159": 1.0, "15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227": 0.5}}, {"text": "Egypt has achieved a balance despite the Corona pandemic, attracting investment due to its available labor and infrastructure projects.", "citations": {"15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt ranked seventh in foreign direct investment inflows in 2020, receiving $327 million and 43 new projects.", "citations": {"15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227": 1.0, "0f9dd226-d49d-4047-9d6b-49e3c777052d_8070748": 0.5}}, {"text": "In 2020, FDI created 6,000 jobs in Egypt, contributing to 3.5% economic growth, with the country's GDP reaching $362 billion.", "citations": {"0f9dd226-d49d-4047-9d6b-49e3c777052d_8070748": 1.0}}, {"text": "The African Continental Free Trade Area (AfCFTA) aims to create a single market of 1.3 billion people with a $3.4 trillion GDP, with Egypt leading African countries in foreign investment, receiving $10 billion in 2023.", "citations": {"a948934f-cc3e-4b6b-ba17-7748e34ef2c6_397268782": 1.0, "ebe067f6-e871-4151-8a02-9e48f41ddec5_254214825": 0.5}}, {"text": "TotalEnergies and Chinese mining companies are major foreign investors in Africa, with TotalEnergies investing $10 billion in Uganda and Tanzania, and Chinese companies dominating lithium mining with 83% supply.", "citations": {"b591e5f5-1140-4208-965a-c054ddae4b21_64014529": 1.0, "70db76f2-e430-46d3-8b33-bf6292e4cb3e_1061429741": 0.5}}, {"text": "The Egyptian government has partnered with international companies to localize transport industries and operate ports.", "citations": {"ebe067f6-e871-4151-8a02-9e48f41ddec5_254214825": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investments in Africa have caused significant job loss, such as in Kenya where tea harvesting machines have led to over 10,000 locals losing their jobs.", "citations": {"c071483c-4f7d-4b68-9e6b-40be627e9f0b_37849381": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investments in African private healthcare, totaling $2.4 billion from 2010 to 2022, have led to negative social impacts, including patient imprisonment over unpaid bills.", "citations": {"86d75d5b-4ba6-49e4-a914-b6c1815a5c42_48749163": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investments have had significant environmental impacts, such as lithium mining and the TotalEnergies project in Uganda, which harm local communities and ecosystems.", "citations": {"70db76f2-e430-46d3-8b33-bf6292e4cb3e_1061429741": 1.0, "b591e5f5-1140-4208-965a-c054ddae4b21_64014529": 0.5}}, {"text": "Foreign investments have had mixed economic impacts, with some, like Egypt's $5.1 billion in 2021, contributing to growth.", "citations": {"ae292450-64e9-4526-be1f-0c7555974775_845790495": 1.0}}, {"text": "African countries risk debt traps with Chinese loans, heading towards over-indebtedness.", "citations": {"07673e60-b3da-415b-abc9-3665c6416001_423216995": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign investments in Africa have had complex and multifaceted effects on local communities, with both positive and negative social, economic, and environmental impacts.", "citations": {"07673e60-b3da-415b-abc9-3665c6416001_423216995": 1.0, "23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891": 0.5, "70db76f2-e430-46d3-8b33-bf6292e4cb3e_1061429741": 0.25, "86d75d5b-4ba6-49e4-a914-b6c1815a5c42_48749163": 0.125, "a948934f-cc3e-4b6b-ba17-7748e34ef2c6_397268782": 0.0625, "ae292450-64e9-4526-be1f-0c7555974775_845790495": 0.03125, "b591e5f5-1140-4208-965a-c054ddae4b21_64014529": 0.015625, "c071483c-4f7d-4b68-9e6b-40be627e9f0b_37849381": 0.0078125, "da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125": 0.00390625, "ebe067f6-e871-4151-8a02-9e48f41ddec5_254214825": 0.001953125}}, {"text": "Attracting investments, which requires a clear political vision and respect for international law and sovereignty, contributes to economic growth by increasing productive capacity and transferring technology.", "citations": {"0111c059-224c-4465-9f3c-81a544ba1d22_609690175": 1.0}}, {"text": "National legislations regulate investments to guarantee investor rights, requiring transparency, integrity, and good governance to attract foreign investments.", "citations": {"0111c059-224c-4465-9f3c-81a544ba1d22_609690175": 1.0}}, {"text": "The judiciary provides guarantees to foreign investors through correct law and procedures, and fighting corruption is necessary to attract them.", "citations": {"0111c059-224c-4465-9f3c-81a544ba1d22_609690175": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt needs sacrifices for development, and laws regulating construction should be issued to promote investment and support small enterprises.", "citations": {"1f881c37-eabe-49e3-9a97-4f74716de5fb_831765785": 1.0}}, {"text": "A national strategy and index for foreign direct investment should be established, with the state balancing public and private interests.", "citations": {"1f881c37-eabe-49e3-9a97-4f74716de5fb_831765785": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign direct investment reached $1.65 trillion in 2021, a 77% increase from 2020, as COMESA countries rely on it to overcome economic conditions.", "citations": {"23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891": 1.0}}, {"text": "RIA provides international best practices and crucial services to promote foreign direct investment, which helps improve growth rates in countries.", "citations": {"23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dubai ranked first in attracting foreign direct investment in 2021.", "citations": {"47fdc9b8-f460-4870-99b2-063802f39d52_402269449": 1.0, "660c1a12-bdbf-470e-88ba-7046d4faea0a_609427402": 0.5}}, {"text": "Investment promotion efforts are increased and a good governance system is implemented, with the Ministry of Investment established to promote foreign investment.", "citations": {"660c1a12-bdbf-470e-88ba-7046d4faea0a_609427402": 1.0}}, {"text": "Investing in local resources and optimizing the investment environment can attract foreign investment, create jobs, and generate secondary income.", "citations": {"96e5486a-b9a1-490f-98d2-4a6c79d66536_818576941": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ensuring national treatment and land security, as outlined in Jordan's Investment Environment Law, can promote foreign investment through automatic approval for transactions after 15 days.", "citations": {"9e52df05-aefa-4064-af69-e596a2fc6c6b_69254886": 1.0, "b65af01a-14ae-4ee4-8e81-4b320ccd2b80_99587693": 0.5}}, {"text": "The State Council issued \"Opinions\" to optimize the foreign investment environment, with 29 departments involved, as investment immigration is a common global policy, like Hong Kong's 2003 Capital Investment Entrant Scheme.", "citations": {"c286860f-d67f-4a7f-b18b-ce3cfc378f90_845016267": 1.0, "c2fb166b-fc57-4a5c-b4c6-77dc3c5548d4_217833485": 0.5}}, {"text": "Singapore and Korea offer investment immigration schemes, including government bonds, that benefit both investors and locals.", "citations": {"c2fb166b-fc57-4a5c-b4c6-77dc3c5548d4_217833485": 1.0}}, {"text": "There is limited information on foreign investment in Africa, requiring more research for specific figures and trends.", "citations": {"23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891": 1.0}}, {"text": "It is essential to promote best practices that benefit both investors and local populations through foreign investments.", "citations": {"0111c059-224c-4465-9f3c-81a544ba1d22_609690175": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa's economy has grown 5 percent annually over the past decade, with a large and youthful population of over 1 billion people in sub-Saharan Africa.", "citations": {"100ec187-499c-4e90-9c2e-c8bcbc89b665_79045555": 1.0}}, {"text": "Google will invest $1 billion in Africa, targeting Kenya and Nigeria for digital transformation.", "citations": {"100ec187-499c-4e90-9c2e-c8bcbc89b665_79045555": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mauritius is the top-ranked economy in sub-Saharan Africa for ease of doing business, and Africa leads in technology-led innovation in sectors like banking and telecoms.", "citations": {"100ec187-499c-4e90-9c2e-c8bcbc89b665_79045555": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa has diverse resources, but political instability and conflicts hinder investment and trade.", "citations": {"ea26aacb-88c6-4f9b-b777-714b3d73909e_932614160": 1.0}}, {"text": "Lack of data and poor logistics in Africa hinder investment by making informed decisions difficult and increasing transport costs and risks.", "citations": {"ea26aacb-88c6-4f9b-b777-714b3d73909e_932614160": 1.0}}, {"text": "African countries without payment settlement systems face higher investment risks, but investment laws, guarantees, and economic zones can attract investors.", "citations": {"ea26aacb-88c6-4f9b-b777-714b3d73909e_932614160": 1.0}}, {"text": "Climate change, poverty, corruption, and lack of legal security hinder Africa's economic growth and deter investors, emphasizing the need for improvement.", "citations": {"ef2d18dc-5128-4ccd-a2ed-d61e8e4f4aa1_634219013": 1.0}}, {"text": "Improving access to technology and innovation is crucial for Africa's growth, which can be accelerated by private sector development and global financial architecture reform.", "citations": {"ef2d18dc-5128-4ccd-a2ed-d61e8e4f4aa1_634219013": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa absorbs only 3% of global energy investment, despite 600 million people lacking electricity, due to high capital costs.", "citations": {"4c24943d-0d4b-4104-8c79-992d4cc39a71_108060334": 1.0}}, {"text": "International institutions and private sector financing, including solar power, can help reduce Africa's energy gap and emissions.", "citations": {"4c24943d-0d4b-4104-8c79-992d4cc39a71_108060334": 1.0}}, {"text": "By 2040, 1 billion people will have access to power, but 500 million will remain off the grid, with Nigeria being a risky African business location, albeit with less risk in offshore areas.", "citations": {"cc823868-5925-4e6a-94de-93449571e616_594440946": 1.0}}, {"text": "South Africa has a stable government and infrastructure, making it attractive to investors, and Africa Oil has no debt with a conservative debt ratio of 0.4.", "citations": {"cc823868-5925-4e6a-94de-93449571e616_594440946": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chevron's leases generate cash flow for Africa Oil, but investors should expect irregular distributions.", "citations": {"cc823868-5925-4e6a-94de-93449571e616_594440946": 1.0}}, {"text": "Liberia's commodity-dependent economy makes investment diversification essential, adding 30 percent value.", "citations": {}}], "references": ["ea26aacb-88c6-4f9b-b777-714b3d73909e_932614160", "23cd6320-dc30-49bb-b11d-4e573e59f6db_178038891", "c2fb166b-fc57-4a5c-b4c6-77dc3c5548d4_217833485", "9e52df05-aefa-4064-af69-e596a2fc6c6b_69254886", "4c24943d-0d4b-4104-8c79-992d4cc39a71_108060334", "100ec187-499c-4e90-9c2e-c8bcbc89b665_79045555", "96e5486a-b9a1-490f-98d2-4a6c79d66536_818576941", "c071483c-4f7d-4b68-9e6b-40be627e9f0b_37849381", "cc823868-5925-4e6a-94de-93449571e616_594440946", "ef2d18dc-5128-4ccd-a2ed-d61e8e4f4aa1_634219013", "c286860f-d67f-4a7f-b18b-ce3cfc378f90_845016267", "b591e5f5-1140-4208-965a-c054ddae4b21_64014529", "07673e60-b3da-415b-abc9-3665c6416001_423216995", "660c1a12-bdbf-470e-88ba-7046d4faea0a_609427402", "ae292450-64e9-4526-be1f-0c7555974775_845790495", "15facfa3-0c51-42c1-af64-581c8eb46003_53471227", "b65af01a-14ae-4ee4-8e81-4b320ccd2b80_99587693", "70db76f2-e430-46d3-8b33-bf6292e4cb3e_1061429741", "0f9dd226-d49d-4047-9d6b-49e3c777052d_8070748", "86d75d5b-4ba6-49e4-a914-b6c1815a5c42_48749163", "da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125", "a948934f-cc3e-4b6b-ba17-7748e34ef2c6_397268782", "2d53bcf5-e733-4209-8d61-53b587b8bc19_796995159", "ebe067f6-e87