{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1033", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The global trend towards a 4-day workweek is gaining momentum, with countries like the UAE and Sharjah adopting reduced work hours with full pay.", "citations": {"1ca23fc5-1e30-4aa8-ac99-04ecc30df58b_831866648": 1.0}}, {"text": "About 78% of employees report feeling happier and less stressed with a 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek improves employee well-being and productivity, with companies seeing cost savings and up to a 20% productivity increase.", "citations": {"4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730": 1.0}}, {"text": "Meeting customer demands is a challenge for companies implementing a 4-day workweek, especially in industries like healthcare and customer service.", "citations": {"4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can address challenges by exploring flexible scheduling options, such as working from home or a compact week system.", "citations": {"8008555c-e414-4a82-b475-cd6c05aa50b7_167230380": 1.0}}, {"text": "Technology, like automation and AI, can support a 4-day workweek by streamlining operations and maintaining productivity.", "citations": {"1e67ebc5-2d6b-4a8b-856c-9376ae8a8f68_691825519": 1.0}}, {"text": "Implementing a 4-day workweek requires careful consideration of its benefits and challenges, as well as the needs of diverse employee groups.", "citations": {"e47bad82-5cc3-4d6d-a752-d965ddaf0f26_670974651": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek can lead to improved well-being, productivity, and job satisfaction, as well as cost savings and increased efficiency.", "citations": {"092b9b4a-fc14-4205-98eb-1c1872d911e0_256602758": 1.0, "1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687": 0.5, "2afb54f5-6e6f-4cd6-9856-49054d7f7c21_155420427": 0.25, "35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 0.125,