{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1038", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "The 2020 conversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque sparked controversy and criticism from countries like Greece, the US, Russia, and UNESCO, seen as a political move by President Erdogan.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government defends the decision, citing it as an internal matter, and promises the site will remain open and preserved.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Critics argue that the reconversion reflects Erdogan's efforts to impose Islamic laws and promote a conservative Islamist agenda in Turkey.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "The site's UNESCO World Heritage Site designation has been cited as a reason for criticism, as the reconversion undermines its cultural and historical significance.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan has invoked Sultan Mehmed II, who conquered Constantinople in 1453, as a matter of national pride and historical significance.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia's reconversion has sparked controversy over the growing role of religion in Turkish politics and society.", "citations": {"78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096": 1.0}}, {"text": "The international community has expressed concerns that the reconversion undermines secularism and cultural preservation.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "As a tour guide in Istanbul, be prepared to address tourist concerns about Hagia Sophia's conversion in a sensitive manner.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides provide accurate information about the site's history and cultural significance while respecting its status as a mosque.", "citations": {"4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Knowing the site's history and policies helps tour guides address tourist concerns about the Hagia Sophia conversion.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides should ensure tourists respect the site's status as a mosque by dressing modestly and not disturbing prayers.", "citations": {"4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Effectively communicating Hagia Sophia's significance requires sensitivity and respect for its Christian and Islamic heritage.", "citations": {"78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque may impact local tourism businesses and revenue.", "citations": {"d0d4acd7-74b5-467f-9c78-985c6a08a9e5_893345947": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides must balance historical information with respect for the site's current religious use.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Technology like QR code headsets can provide multilingual information about Hagia Sophia without disrupting prayers.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The site's management plan regulates visitor density to improve quality and safety.", "citations": {"f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides can help visitors understand Hagia Sophia's complex history and cultural significance while respecting its current context.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia now has separate entrances and tourist earphones under a new visitor management policy.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides use headsets with 23 languages to provide information about Hagia Sophia to tourists in their native la