ia mosque, where guides provide historical context.", "citations": {"4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has implemented a visitor management policy with separate entrances and guided earphones for tourists.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides cannot accompany visitors and advance booking is required at least 3 hours prior.", "citations": {"4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign tourists pay a \u20ac25 entrance fee, while Turkish citizens enter for free.", "citations": {"5f313598-c9ac-40a3-8bae-106d6564ae87_210914181": 1.0}}, {"text": "Guides speak multiple languages and provide information in 23 languages through headset guides with QR codes.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "UNESCO has criticized the conversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque and recommended a visitor management plan.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish Tourism Minister aims to preserve the site's cultural significance while managing tourist expectations.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tourists can visit the site safely and respectfully due to security cameras and emergency systems.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides should provide historical facts, answer questions, and be sensitive to tourists' differing opinions and emotions.", "citations": {"4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879": 1.0}}, {"text": "The site's complex history requires knowledgeable and empathetic tour guides.", "citations": {"d0d4acd7-74b5-467f-9c78-985c6a08a9e5_893345947": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Culture and Tourism provides training for tour guides on cultural heritage sites like Hagia Sophia.", "citations": {"aa2cea5d-6f19-4968-a97b-bdf3f195340e_9004