{"metadata": {"team_id": "encourage", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1067", "run_id": "encourage-crop"}, "responses": [{"text": "Robotic pets are being marketed as emotional companions to provide comfort and reduce loneliness, especially for the elderly or lonely.", "citations": {"18de596d-601d-4044-9f4c-7c5cff4aae60_686667879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Robotic pets provide companionship without maintenance worries and are used in hospice care by nonprofits like Capital Caring.", "citations": {"18de596d-601d-4044-9f4c-7c5cff4aae60_686667879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Robotic pets, like Boston Dynamics' dogs, can provide sarcastic and informative responses to questions.", "citations": {"2a379fa7-3305-4fba-abc7-626ff34c04b5_753972222": 1.0}}, {"text": "They can be used in logistics, households, hospitals, and by the New York Police for tasks such as crime scene screening and patient communication.", "citations": {"2a379fa7-3305-4fba-abc7-626ff34c04b5_753972222": 1.0}}, {"text": "Robotic pets can cost between $100 and $2,774, with some models funded largely through donations.", "citations": {"18de596d-601d-4044-9f4c-7c5cff4aae60_686667879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Robotic pets can reduce loneliness by 70 percent and pain by 75 percent, improving seniors' cardiovascular health, anxiety, mood, and quality of life.", "citations": {"567156d1-0ff2-40fe-908b-b47b5cfd0fd1_99665050": 1.0, "6a873279-c9a2-4442-8cc2-8b258cf59e4d_842687117": 0.5}}, {"text": "The use of robotic pets raises ethical questions about replacing real animals and potential over-reliance.", "citations": {"c7f55dcc-7139-4a18-95bb-5898d9544a17_162742656": 1.0}}, {"text": "More research is needed to understand the benefits and risks of using robotic pets in therapy and social settings.", "citations": {"c7f55dcc-7139-4a18-95bb-5898d9544a17_162742656": 1.0}}, {"text": "Robotic pets can give seniors a sense of purpose and nostalgic comfort.", "citations": {"6a873279-c9a2-4442-8cc2-8b258cf59e4d_842687117": 1.0}}, {"text": "They can reduce anxiety and agitation in people with Alzheimer's and dementia, and provide comfort to children and veterans.", "citations": {"97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422": 1.0, "f6c4d9f5-3d53-40be-a179-1a1c885aeb15_759605853": 0.5}}, {"text": "Robotic pets have numerous benefits in therapeutic settings, including reducing social isolation and improving elderly individuals' quality of life.", "citations": {"807bfe6e-889d-4f05-ac83-bac40ada16b9_282342600": 1.0}}, {"text": "Robotic pets should be used alongside human interaction, not in place of it, to prevent over-reliance and mitigate risks.", "citations": {"6d5911bf-c685-4696-ba7d-e8d4ba6d6c1f_777023714": 1.0}}, {"text": "Robotic pets can provide significant benefits in therapeutic and social settings, but their use must be managed responsibly to mitigate potential risks.", "citations": {"18de596d-601d-4044-9f4c-7c5cff4aae60_686667879": 1.0, "567156d1-0ff2-40fe-908b-b47b5cfd0fd1_99665050": 0.5, "6a873279-c9a2-4442-8cc2-8b258cf59e4d_842687117": 0.25, "97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422": 0.125, "f6c4d9f5-3d53-40be-a179-1a1c885aeb15_759605853": 0.0625}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"2a379fa7-3305-4fba-abc7-626ff34c04b5_753972222": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"3d175958-95bc-43fe-88e1-e71e09541389_369000232": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"436f6dca-3571-4e87-b474-e70ec06c96ce_887925875": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"683d920a-717e-458d-997b-97c42fa52075_217671007": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"daaa2d55-82b5-47a4-acfb-4aa775ba6971_982434132": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"ecda5beb-b251-436a-95f3-d622ecdf24c8_761197108": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"6d2add10-c7c0-456c-9771-db9737f3035e_1072648350": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"728b791f-977a-44bc-aa11-5be625f1fcae_205612430": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"cc223e0f-9093-43f6-9a6d-d16e46c4df37_332570794": 1.0}}, {"text": ".", "citations": {"d44fc164-774c-4d4d-b0f5-c1f704bdc75a_76208305": 1.0}}, {"tex